NK005(ca)006:1: gi cho ga byin rlabs char 'bebs zhes bya ba
NK005(ca)006:3: dpal sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam par sbyor ba'i dbang
NK005(ca)006:4: gi cho ga byin rlabs char 'bebs zhes bya ba
NK005(ca)006:5: / dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK005(ca)006:6: bde chen 'gyur med dpal ldan rdo rje 'chang //
NK005(ca)006:7: stong nyid kun bzang dga' mar mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK005(ca)006:8: rnam rol rigs drug 'khor lo'i phyag rgya yis //
NK005(ca)006:9: srid zhir rgyas 'debs dpal ldan bla mar 'dud //
NK005(ca)006:10: sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam par sbyor ba yi //
NK005(ca)006:11: snying po'i dkyil 'khor mchog tu bkri ba'i thabs //
NK005(ca)006:12: dbang bskur cho ga dam pa'i zhal lung bzhin //
NK005(ca)006:13: byin rlabs char du 'bebs pa'i dpyid du spel //
NK005(ca)006:14: de yang 'dir sangs rgyas thams cad dang mnyam par
NK005(ca)006:15: sbyor ba'i dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba'i cho ga
NK005(ca)006:17: dkyil 'khor sngon du 'gro ba can yin te /
NK005(ca)006:19: sa gzhi sta gon gnas pa dang //
NK005(ca)006:20: gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor rtsol sgrub cing //
NK005(ca)006:21: 'jig pa sbyin sreg gtor ma'i las //
NK005(ca)006:22: rab gnas dbang bskur la sogs rnams //
NK005(ca)006:23: bdag gzhan smin cing grol ba'i phyir //
NK005(ca)006:24: dam pa'i lung bzhin sgrub par bya //
NK005(ca)006:25: zhes gsungs pa bzhin shes par byas la /
NK005(ca)006:26: sa'i cho ga dang sta gon gyi cho ga gzhan dang /
NK005(ca)006:28: sgrub cing mchod pa la sogs rnams kyi dkyil chog las shes pa'i dbang du byas nas /
NK005(ca)006:29: 'dir slob mar dbang bskur ba'i cho ga la /
NK005(ca)006:30: sbyor ba sta gon gyi cho ga dang /
NK005(ca)006:31: dngos gzhi dbang bskur ba'i cho ga'o //
NK005(ca)006:33: lha sta gon gyi rjes sam /
NK005(ca)006:34: de dang bum pa sta gon sbrel ba'i rjes nyid du'am /
NK005(ca)006:35: dngos gzhi'i dkyil 'khor bshom bkod zin nas nang par
NK005(ca)006:36: dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa byed rgyu'i nyin snga ma'i
NK005(ca)006:37: dgong kha'i dus su byed kyang rung ste /
NK005(ca)006:38: de ltar na dkyil 'khor sgrub rdzas rnams yol bas bsgribs te mi mthong bar byas /
NK005(ca)006:39: slob dpon gyi nye logs su /
NK005(ca)006:48: dri dang bcas pa rnams bshams nas /
NK005(ca)006:49: cho ga dngos la bcu gsum las /
NK005(ca)006:50: dang po spro ba bskyed pa ni /
NK005(ca)006:51: mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'i slob ma rnams phyi rol du khrus bya /
NK005(ca)006:52: de nas slob dpon gyis chos bshad thun mong ba rnams sngon du 'gro bas /
NK005(ca)006:53: mtshams sbyor gyi khyad par 'di ni sku gsung thugs
NK005(ca)006:54: yon tan phrin las lnga'i gzhi dang rtsa bar gyur
NK005(ca)006:56: sku'i rgyud thams cad kyi gzhi dang rtsa bar gyur
NK005(ca)006:57: pa dpal sangs rgyas thams cad dang mnyam par sbyor
NK005(ca)006:58: ba'i chos kyi rnam grangs te /
NK005(ca)006:59: de la'ang smin grol gyi rim pa gnyis su yod pa las /
NK005(ca)006:60: 'dir smin byed kyi dbang nyid bskur ba skabs su babs pa yin zhing /
NK005(ca)006:61: dbang de la'ang sbyor dngos rjes gsum las skabs 'dir
NK005(ca)006:62: sbyor ba sta gon gyi bye brag slob ma lhag
NK005(ca)006:63: par gnas pa'i chos rnams sgrub par byed pa yin
NK005(ca)006:64: pas / de'i slad du thog mar khyed rang rnams
NK005(ca)006:65: kyi lus longs spyod dus gsum dang 'brel ba'i dge
NK005(ca)006:66: tshogs rgya mtsho dang bcas pa thams cad gcig tu
NK005(ca)006:67: bsdoms nas 'bul ba'i mos 'dun bgyis te zhing khams
NK005(ca)006:68: pas / 'bul mdzod / ces mtshams sbyar te /
NK005(ca)006:69: phyag sngon du 'gro bas man+dala phul nas /
NK005(ca)006:70: me tog dang bcas pa'i thal mo sbyar te 'dug
NK005(ca)006:71: pa la slob dpon gyis 'di skad ces brjod par
NK005(ca)006:72: bya'o // bu tshur theg pa chen po la //
NK005(ca)006:73: khyod ni tshul chen snod yin te //
NK005(ca)006:74: gsang sngags spyod tshul cho ga ni //
NK005(ca)006:75: khyod la yang dag bstan par bya //
NK005(ca)006:76: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas gang 'das dang //
NK005(ca)006:77: de bzhin gang dag ma byon dang //
NK005(ca)006:78: da ltar byung ba'i rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK005(ca)006:79: 'gro la phan phyir gnas bzhugs pa //
NK005(ca)006:80: de kun gsang sngags zab mo yi //
NK005(ca)006:81: cho ga bzang po 'di mkhyen nas //
NK005(ca)006:82: dpa' bo byang chub shing drung du //
NK005(ca)006:83: thams cad mkhyen pa mtshan med brnyes //
NK005(ca)006:84: gsang sngags sbyor ba mnyam med pa //
NK005(ca)006:85: bcom ldan rigs drug dkyil 'khor gyis //
NK005(ca)006:86: bdud sde shin tu mi bzad pa'i //
NK005(ca)006:87: dpung chen mtha' dag rnam bcom pas //
NK005(ca)006:88: de bas kun mkhyen thob bya'i phyir //
NK005(ca)006:89: bu yi blo gros 'di gyis shig /
NK005(ca)006:91: de rnams kyi don yang bshad /
NK005(ca)006:92: gnyis pa rjes su gdams pa ni /
NK005(ca)006:93: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun la //
NK005(ca)006:94: rtag tu skyabs su 'gro bar gyis //
NK005(ca)006:96: rigs kyi dkyil 'khor so so'i phyir //
NK005(ca)006:97: 'khor lor bzhugs pa'i bdag nyid rnams //
NK005(ca)006:98: kun la skyabs su 'gro bar gyis //
NK005(ca)006:99: dpa' bo dpa' mo 'khor bcas dang //
NK005(ca)006:100: byang chub sems dpa' bdag nyid che //
NK005(ca)006:101: khyad par du yang slob dpon la //
NK005(ca)006:102: khyod kyis skyabs su 'gro bar gyis //
NK005(ca)006:105: ma lus phyogs na bzhugs pa yi //
NK005(ca)006:106: dkyil 'khor bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK005(ca)006:107: bdag gis dus 'di nas bzung ste //
NK005(ca)006:108: ji srid snying por byang chub bar //
NK005(ca)006:109: de yi tshangs spyod gnyis med par //
NK005(ca)006:110: bdag gis sdom pa ma lus bzung //
NK005(ca)006:112: bzhi pa tshogs bsags pa ni /
NK005(ca)006:113: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK005(ca)006:114: dkon mchog gsum po bzung bar bgyi //
NK005(ca)006:115: bdag gis sdig pa bgyis pa dang //
NK005(ca)006:116: bgyid stsal rjes su yi rang ba //
NK005(ca)006:117: mgon po'i spyan sngar mchis nas su //
NK005(ca)006:118: de dag thams cad bshags par bgyi //
NK005(ca)006:119: rgyas ba sras bcas thams cad dang //
NK005(ca)006:120: rang rgyal dgra bcom 'gro rnams kyi //
NK005(ca)006:121: bsgom bzlas la sogs bsod nams la //
NK005(ca)006:122: dad pas rjes su yi rang ngo //
NK005(ca)006:123: sems nyid mngon par sangs rgyas dang //
NK005(ca)006:124: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor byed cing //
NK005(ca)006:125: tshogs spyod byang chub sems dpa' la //
NK005(ca)006:126: bdag ni gus pas skyabs su mchi //
NK005(ca)006:127: sangs rgyas rnams 'byung ji lta bar //
NK005(ca)006:128: skal ldan byang chub sems dpa' yis //
NK005(ca)006:129: byang chub thugs mchog rgya chen po //
NK005(ca)006:130: 'gro ba rgya chen don la dmigs //
NK005(ca)006:131: ma lus phyogs bzhugs dkyil 'khor gyi //
NK005(ca)006:132: mgon rnams bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK005(ca)006:133: dus 'di nyid nas sangs rgyas bar //
NK005(ca)006:134: bla med rgya chen dad pas gzigs //
NK005(ca)006:135: zhes lan gsum gyis rgyud dag par bya'o //
NK005(ca)006:136: lnga pa sdom pa bzung ba ni /
NK005(ca)006:137: ji ltar dus gsum mgon po rnams //
NK005(ca)006:138: byang chub tu ni nges mdzad pa'i //
NK005(ca)006:139: byang chub sems ni bla na med //
NK005(ca)006:140: dam pa bdag gis bskyed par bgyi //
NK005(ca)006:141: tshul khrims kyi ni bslab pa dang //
NK005(ca)006:142: dge ba'i chos ni sdud pa dang //
NK005(ca)006:143: sems can don byed tshul khrims gsum //
NK005(ca)006:144: bdag gis brtan por gzung bar bgyi //
NK005(ca)006:145: sangs rgyas rnal 'byor sdom pa la //
NK005(ca)006:146: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun te //
NK005(ca)006:147: bla na med pa'i dkon mchog gsum //
NK005(ca)006:148: deng nas brtsams te bzung bar bgyi //
NK005(ca)006:149: rdo rje rigs mchog chen po la //
NK005(ca)006:150: rdo rje dril bu phyag rgya yang //
NK005(ca)006:151: yang dag nyid du gzung bar bgyi //
NK005(ca)006:152: slob dpon dag kyang gzung bar bgyi //
NK005(ca)006:153: rin chen rigs mchog chen po yi //
NK005(ca)006:154: dam tshig yid du 'ong ba la //
NK005(ca)006:155: nyin re zhing ni lan drug tu //
NK005(ca)006:156: sbyin pa rnam bzhi rab tu sbyin //
NK005(ca)006:157: byang chub chen po las byung ba'i //
NK005(ca)006:158: pad+ma'i rigs chen dag pa la //
NK005(ca)006:159: phyi nang gsang ba'i theg pa gsum //
NK005(ca)006:160: dam pa'i chos ni gzung bar bgyi //
NK005(ca)006:161: las kyi rigs mchog chen po la //
NK005(ca)006:162: sdom pa thams cad ldan par ni //
NK005(ca)006:163: yang dag nyid du gzung bar bgyi //
NK005(ca)006:164: mchod pa'i las kyang ci nus bgyi //
NK005(ca)006:165: byang chub sems ni bla med pa //
NK005(ca)006:166: dam pa bdag gis bskyed bgyis nas //
NK005(ca)006:167: sems can kun gyi don gyi phyir //
NK005(ca)006:168: bdag gis sdom pa ma lus gzung //
NK005(ca)006:169: ma grol bar ni dgrol bar bgyi //
NK005(ca)006:170: ma bsgral ba rnams bsgral bar bgyi //
NK005(ca)006:171: dbugs ma byin pa dbyugs dbyung zhing //
NK005(ca)006:174: dge ba'i las rnams 'di dag gis //
NK005(ca)006:176: 'khor ba'i rgya mtshor bying ba rnams //
NK005(ca)006:177: bla med byang chub 'god par bgyi //
NK005(ca)006:178: zhes lan gsum gyis sdom pa bzung ngo //
NK005(ca)006:179: drug pa byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK005(ca)006:180: slob ma'i gnas gsum du dri bzang gi chus thig le byas te /
NK005(ca)006:181: spyi bor 'khor lor lte bar dkar po /
NK005(ca)006:182: mgrin par pad+ma'i lte bar +aahdamara po /
NK005(ca)006:183: snying gar rdo rje'i lte bar h+aum sngon pos mtshan pa dang /
NK005(ca)006:184: slar yang rdo rjes reg nas /
NK005(ca)006:185: +aahh+aum gis lha gnas byas te brtan par bya'o //
NK005(ca)006:187: de ltar byin gyis brlabs pa ni mchod pa'i gnas
NK005(ca)006:188: su gyur pa yin pas de'i spyi bor me tog
NK005(ca)006:189: / mdun du spos dang mar me /
NK005(ca)006:190: snying gar dri rnams phul bar mos la /
NK005(ca)006:191: pa na bem pe nu su ra to ti pu
NK005(ca)006:192: ra muhsarba ta th+aa ga ta sid+d+hi hu sa ma
NK005(ca)006:193: yo ta mi sarba ma h+aa su kha sid+d+hi hu
NK005(ca)006:194: / sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga d+h+au pe d+h+au /
NK005(ca)006:198: zhes so so'i sngags kyis dbul lo //
NK005(ca)006:199: brgyad pa so shing sbyin pa ni /
NK005(ca)006:200: dngos grub kyi ltas brtags pa'i phyir /
NK005(ca)006:201: bla ma'i mdun gyi sa der ba byung lngas khru
NK005(ca)006:202: gang gru bzhir byugs pa'i man+dala la me tog gi
NK005(ca)006:203: tshom bu dgu bkod nas slob ma kha shar du
NK005(ca)006:204: phyogs pa la / u dum+wa ra la sogs 'o
NK005(ca)006:205: ma can gyi so shing srin bug med pa sor
NK005(ca)006:206: bcu gnyis pa'i rtse mor me tog bcings pa rigs
NK005(ca)006:207: sngags kyi byin gyis brlabs nas dngos grub kyi dmod
NK005(ca)006:209: des kyang so shing gi rtse mos so drug cing /
NK005(ca)006:212: zhes brjod cing tshom bu'i steng du dor bas /
NK005(ca)006:213: me tog gis bcings pa'i rtse mo bdag dang steng ngos su bltas na dngos grub mchog /
NK005(ca)006:215: mtshams dang byang du 'jig rten pa /
NK005(ca)006:217: phyogs bzhir zhi sogs kyi dngos grub 'grub par lung bstan no //
NK005(ca)006:218: dgu pa khyor chu blud pa ni /
NK005(ca)006:220: las thams cad pa bzlas pa'i dri bzang gi chu lag par sbyin te /
NK005(ca)006:221: h+r+aihbi shud+d+ha sarba d+har+m+aa p+aa pam ni ts+aa sh+ya bi
NK005(ca)006:222: sho d+ha ya sarba bi kalpa a pa n+aa ya
NK005(ca)006:224: khyor ba dang pos kha bshal /
NK005(ca)006:227: bcu pa ku sha gtod pa ni /
NK005(ca)006:228: rmi lam rno bar bya ba'i phyir ku sha sngo ljang rtse mo ma nyams pa che chung gnyis /
NK005(ca)006:234: sarba turte ku ru ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK005(ca)006:235: zhes pas byin gyis brlabs pa sngas dang stan du sbyin no //
NK005(ca)006:236: bcu gcig pa srung skud gdags pa ni /
NK005(ca)006:237: rmi lam gyi bar chad bsal ba'i phyir srung skud
NK005(ca)006:238: srid du lus tshad sum sgril spoms su ku sha'i
NK005(ca)006:239: sum 'gyur rdo rje'i mdud pa gsum ldan dang rigs
NK005(ca)006:240: kyi sngags dang 'bru gsum gyis basngagasa pa pho'i dpung
NK005(ca)006:241: pa g.yon dang mo'i g.yas su bcings te chu dang
NK005(ca)006:242: bcas pa'i rdo rje rgya gram du reg pas bsrung
NK005(ca)006:243: bar bya'o // bcu gnyis pa chos bshad pa ni /
NK005(ca)006:244: zab mo'i lam la spro ba bskyed pa de nyid brtan par bya ba'i phyir te /
NK005(ca)006:245: 'jig rten du ni kun mkhyen dag /
NK005(ca)006:246: u dum+wa ra'i me tog bzhin //
NK005(ca)006:247: brgya lam na ni ris 'ga' zhig /
NK005(ca)006:249: gsang sngags spyod pa'i tshul 'byung ba //
NK005(ca)006:250: de bas kyang ni dkon pa ste //
NK005(ca)006:251: gang gis sems can mnyam med don //
NK005(ca)006:252: bla med byed par nus pa yin //
NK005(ca)006:255: bskal pa bye ba du ma ru //
NK005(ca)006:256: sngon du sdig pa byas pa gang //
NK005(ca)006:258: de dag zad pa gyur yin na //
NK005(ca)006:259: grags pa mtha' yas sngags spyod pa'i //
NK005(ca)006:260: tshul la gnas na smos ci dgos //
NK005(ca)006:262: mdor na gsang sngags kyi tshul 'di ni dkon la
NK005(ca)006:263: phan yon che ba yin pas blo ma 'gyur bar
NK005(ca)006:264: nyams len la brtson par gyis shig /
NK005(ca)006:266: bcu gsum pa rmi lam brtags pa ni /
NK005(ca)006:267: sta gon gyi gnas de nyid du mchod gtor phul
NK005(ca)006:268: nas sngar gyi ku sha'i sngas stan la mi smra
NK005(ca)006:269: zhing dge ba'i sems kyis seng+ge'i nyal stabs kyis nyal
NK005(ca)006:270: nas rmi lam brtag tu bcug nas /
NK005(ca)006:271: slob dpon nang du zhugs te mnyam par bzhag la dkyil 'khor la mchod bstod bya /
NK005(ca)006:272: nangs par rmi lam dris te bzang na dngos grub lung bstan cing spro ba bskyed /
NK005(ca)006:273: ngan na sbyin sreg dang gtor ma dang sngags dang
NK005(ca)006:274: phyag rgyas sbyang zhing ba byung dang dri bzang gi
NK005(ca)006:275: chu sngags kyis sbyangs bas bkru /
NK005(ca)006:276: nam mkha' dbyings phyug ma'i phyag rgya dang /
NK005(ca)006:277: d+har+m+aa d+ha tu swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK005(ca)006:278: zhes pas byin gyis brlab par bya ste /
NK005(ca)006:279: de dag ni sta gon gyi cho ga'o //
NK005(ca)006:280: gnyis pa dngos gzhi dbang bskur ba la /
NK005(ca)006:284: slob mar dbang bskur ba dang bzhi las /
NK005(ca)006:285: dang po gnyis dkyil chog las shes /
NK005(ca)006:286: gsum pa bdag nyid 'jug pa ni /
NK005(ca)006:287: sgrub mchod kyi dgong ka'i dus su bdag nyid bsrung zhing khrus bya /
NK005(ca)006:289: rgyan btags nas stan la 'khod de /
NK005(ca)006:290: slob dpon gyi bya ba rnams bla ma dang tha
NK005(ca)006:291: mi dad pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bos mdzad par
NK005(ca)006:292: bsam ste / 'chad par 'gyur ba bzhin 'jug pa nas brtsams te /
NK005(ca)006:295: gtso bo las he ru ka zhal gcig phyag gnyis
NK005(ca)006:296: pa las kyi rdo rje'i tshul du dbye bas mdzad
NK005(ca)006:297: par bsam mo // de nas dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor
NK005(ca)006:298: lo 'dod chags chen po las byung ba'i de kho
NK005(ca)006:299: na nyid bde ba chen po'i rang bzhin can gzugs
NK005(ca)006:300: brnyan bzhin shes nas slob ma gzhug pa'i phyir //
NK005(ca)006:301: nam mkha' las byung mtshan ldan phyir //
NK005(ca)006:302: thogs ma mtha' ma med pa'i dbyings //
NK005(ca)006:303: rdo rje sems dpa' che rang bzhin //
NK005(ca)006:304: rigs mchog mgon por bdag sgrub mdzod //
NK005(ca)006:305: dngos grub chen po kun gyi mchog /
NK005(ca)006:306: dbang phyug chen po lhag pa'i lha //
NK005(ca)006:307: rdo rje 'dzin pa kun gyi rgyal //
NK005(ca)006:308: mi 'gyur mchog tu bdag sgrubs shig /
NK005(ca)006:309: nyes pa mi mnga' rtag pa ste //
NK005(ca)006:310: 'dod chags kun gyi rjes su chags //
NK005(ca)006:311: 'dod chags chen po dag pa ste //
NK005(ca)006:312: bcom ldan de nyid kyis sgrub mdzod //
NK005(ca)006:313: shin tu dag pa kun gyi mchog /
NK005(ca)006:314: gdod nas grol ba de bzhin gshegs //
NK005(ca)006:315: kun tu bzang po kun gyi bdag /
NK005(ca)006:316: byang chub mchog tu bdag sgrubs shig /
NK005(ca)006:317: dngos grub chen po kun gyi rgyal //
NK005(ca)006:318: dbang phyug chen po phyag rgya'i mchog /
NK005(ca)006:319: grub pa'i rdo rje cher bstod pa //
NK005(ca)006:320: rdo rje can bdag tu sgrubs shig /
NK005(ca)006:321: sems can kun gyi yid khyab pa //
NK005(ca)006:322: sems can kun gyi snying la gnas //
NK005(ca)006:323: sems can kun gyi yab nyid de //
NK005(ca)006:324: 'dod chags bral ba'i dam tshig mchog /
NK005(ca)006:327: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta ban+d+ha nam ka ro mi //
NK005(ca)006:328: rdo rje sems dpa' bsdus pa na //
NK005(ca)006:329: rdo rje rin chen bla na med //
NK005(ca)006:330: rdo rje chos ni glur blangs pas //
NK005(ca)006:331: rdo rje las kun byed par 'gyur //
NK005(ca)006:334: badz+ra +aa lo ke h+r+aih badz+ra gan+d+he h+aam /
NK005(ca)006:336: +amohbadz+ra a ha ra h+r+aih na mahsarba ta th+aa ga
NK005(ca)006:337: te b+h+yo a lang+ka ra pa na bee h+aum s+w+aa
NK005(ca)006:338: h+aa / b+h+yo d+h+yam rat+na me g+ha s+pha ra na h+aum /
NK005(ca)006:339: na mahsarba pany+tsa r+aa sa ya na a mri te h+aum phata /
NK005(ca)006:340: bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su kha h+aum /
NK005(ca)006:341: bla ma sangs rgyas chos dge 'dun //
NK005(ca)006:342: byang chub sems dpa' rnams la yang //
NK005(ca)006:343: rnam kun btud de skyabs mchi zhing //
NK005(ca)006:345: ces glu gar mchod bstod dang bcas pas mnyes par byas nas /
NK005(ca)006:347: shes rab thabs bdag dkyil 'khor mchog /
NK005(ca)006:348: bden pa'i byin rlabs chen po yis //
NK005(ca)006:349: mgon tshogs sprul pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi //
NK005(ca)006:350: 'dod pa thams cad skong byed shog /
NK005(ca)006:351: chos rnams gzugs brnyan lta bu ste //
NK005(ca)006:352: gsal zhing dag la rnyog pa med //
NK005(ca)006:353: gzung 'dzin rab spangs brjod du med //
NK005(ca)006:354: rgyu dang rkyen las byung ba dag /
NK005(ca)006:355: chos nyid de bzhin nyid las byung //
NK005(ca)006:356: bden pa de yis dkyil 'khor ni //
NK005(ca)006:357: gzugs brnyan gsal ba dri med gnas //
NK005(ca)006:358: sems can kun gyis mthong bar shog /
NK005(ca)006:359: ces bden pa'i stobs brjod de dngos grub gsol bar bya'o //
NK005(ca)006:361: shes rab thabs bdag ces pas man chad brjod pas kyang chog go //
NK005(ca)006:364: +aam badz+ra sa ma ya +aamh h+aum badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum /
NK005(ca)006:365: s+w+aa badz+ra sa ma ya s+w+aa /
NK005(ca)006:366: h+aa badz+ra sa ma ya h+aa /
NK005(ca)006:367: zhes rig pa'i me tog dor nas //
NK005(ca)006:368: ye shes rgyal po sku gsung thugs //
NK005(ca)006:369: yon tan phrin las rmad po che //
NK005(ca)006:370: de nyid du ni mnyam sbyor bas //
NK005(ca)006:371: phyag rgya chen por bdag sbyor cig /
NK005(ca)006:374: badz+ra sa ma ya hoh zhes pas bdag nyid dkyil
NK005(ca)006:375: 'khor du zhugs nas slob ma gzhug par gsol ba
NK005(ca)006:376: gdab pa nyid kyis kyang 'grub ste /
NK005(ca)006:377: rigs mthun gyi gsang ba spyi'i cho ga yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK005(ca)006:378: bzhi pa slob mar dbang bskur ba la 'jug pa dang /
NK005(ca)006:380: 'jug pa la phyi nang gnyis kyi phyi 'jug la bzhi las /
NK005(ca)006:382: yol ba'i phyi rol du rgyud dag pa'i slob ma rnams las bum gyi chus bsang /
NK005(ca)006:383: me tog la sogs mchod pa bzhis mchod nas /
NK005(ca)006:384: 'o ma nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sems can thams
NK005(ca)006:385: cad kyi don du rnam pa kun gyi mchog dang
NK005(ca)006:386: ldan pa'i sangs rgyas chos kyi sku gang zhig tshe
NK005(ca)006:388: de'i ched du gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i lam
NK005(ca)006:389: gyi 'jug sgo dang po smin byed dbang gi rim
NK005(ca)006:390: pa rnams legs par nod nas lam zab mo bskyed
NK005(ca)006:391: rdzogs kyi rim pa gnyis la tshul bzhin du bslab
NK005(ca)006:392: par bagyi'o snyam pas byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed
NK005(ca)006:394: chos nyan pa'i kun tu spyod pa rnams kyang blang dor ma 'dzol bar bgyis te /
NK005(ca)006:396: de la gang zhig gsan par bya ba'i chos kyi
NK005(ca)006:397: rnam grangs kyang spyir bdag cag gi ston pa thabs
NK005(ca)006:398: la mkhas shing thugs rje chen po dang ldan pa
NK005(ca)006:399: de nyid kyis gdul bya'i sems can rnams kyi khams
NK005(ca)006:401: bsam pa'i rjes su 'gro ba'i chos kyi 'khor lo
NK005(ca)006:402: dpag tu med pa zhig bskor bar mdzad pa yin
NK005(ca)006:403: yang / re zhig spang gnyen gyi sgo nas bsdu na /
NK005(ca)006:404: gdul bya'i rgyud kyi nyon mongs pa'i bye brag brgyad
NK005(ca)006:405: khri bzhi stong gi gnyen por chos kyi phung po'ang
NK005(ca)006:406: de snyed gcig tu grangs nges pa yin te /
NK005(ca)006:408: kun byed rgyal po'i rgyud las /
NK005(ca)006:409: 'dod chags 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK005(ca)006:410: 'dul ba'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK005(ca)006:411: zhe sdang 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK005(ca)006:412: mdo sde'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK005(ca)006:413: gti mug 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK005(ca)006:414: mngon pa'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK005(ca)006:415: thams cad 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK005(ca)006:416: sde snod bzhi pa nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK005(ca)006:417: mdor na brgyad khri bzhi stong gsungs pa kun //
NK005(ca)006:418: nyon mongs 'dul ba'i gnyen par gsungs par zad //
NK005(ca)006:420: de yang gzhung dang man ngag tsam gyi sgo nas bsdu na /
NK005(ca)006:421: gzhung mtshan nyid phar phyin gyi theg pa dang /
NK005(ca)006:422: man ngag gsang chen rdo rje'i theg pa gnyis su 'du ba yin te /
NK005(ca)006:424: theg pa rnam pa gnyis yin te //
NK005(ca)006:425: mtshan nyid rgyu yi theg pa dang //
NK005(ca)006:430: don gcig na yang ma rmongs dang //
NK005(ca)006:431: thabs mang dka' ba med pa dang //
NK005(ca)006:432: dbang po rnon po'i dbang byas nas //
NK005(ca)006:433: sngags kyi theg pa khyad par 'phags //
NK005(ca)006:434: zhes bshad pa ltar khyad chos bzhi'i sgo nas khyad
NK005(ca)006:435: par du 'phags pa gsang sngags rdo rje'i theg pa
NK005(ca)006:436: nyid yin zhing / de la yang shes byed rgyud
NK005(ca)006:437: sde'i rnam grangs bsam gyis mi khyab pa zhig yod
NK005(ca)006:438: kyang lta spyod tsam gyi sgo nas bsdu na /
NK005(ca)006:439: spyod pa gtso bor ston pa bya ba'i rgyud dang /
NK005(ca)006:440: lta ba gtso bor ston pa rnal 'byor gyi rgyud
NK005(ca)006:441: de gnyis su gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde mtha' dag
NK005(ca)006:443: der yang rnal 'byor gyi rgyud tsam dang /
NK005(ca)006:444: rnal 'byor bla na med pa'i rgyud gnyis su yod pa las //
NK005(ca)006:445: 'di ni rnal 'byor bla na med pa la nang
NK005(ca)006:446: gses bskyed rdzogs rdzogs chen gsum ston pa'i gzhung rgyud
NK005(ca)006:447: lung man ngag gsum yod pa'i dang po rgyud ma
NK005(ca)006:448: h+aa yo ga / de la'ang bskyed rim thabs kyi
NK005(ca)006:449: cha dang rdzogs rim rlung gtso bor byed pas gsal
NK005(ca)006:450: stong rnam par mi rtog pa'i tshul gyis nyams su
NK005(ca)006:451: len pa ma h+aa'i ma h+aa ste pha rgyud gsang
NK005(ca)006:452: ba 'dus pa la sogs pa dang /
NK005(ca)006:453: bskyed rim gyi spros pa shas chung zhing shes rab
NK005(ca)006:454: rdzogs pa'i rim pa khams byang chub kyi sems theg
NK005(ca)006:455: le gtso bor byed pas bde stong rnam par mi
NK005(ca)006:456: rtog pa'i tshul du nyams su len pa ma h+aa'i
NK005(ca)006:457: a nu ste ma rgyud sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor dang
NK005(ca)006:458: dpal yang dag la sogs pa dang /
NK005(ca)006:459: bskyed rdzogs zung du 'jug cing de'ang rdzogs rim rtsa
NK005(ca)006:460: thig rlung gsum las bskyed pa'i bde gsal rnam par
NK005(ca)006:461: mi rtog pa'i ye shes dang /
NK005(ca)006:462: khyad par 'od gsal ye shes chen po la gtso
NK005(ca)006:463: bor byed pa'i tshul gyis nyams su len pa ma
NK005(ca)006:464: h+aa'i a ti ste gnyis med kyi rgyud sgyu 'phrul
NK005(ca)006:465: d+r+wa ba la sogs pa las /
NK005(ca)006:466: 'dir snga 'gyur bka' ma'i bka' srol sku gsung thugs
NK005(ca)006:467: yon tan phrin las lnga'i gzhi dang rtsa bar gyur
NK005(ca)006:468: pa'i rgyud sde lnga las sku'i rgyud thams cad kyi
NK005(ca)006:469: gzhi dang rtsa bar gyur pa ma h+aa'i a nu
NK005(ca)006:470: ste rnal 'byor ma'i rgyud dpal sangs rgyas thams cad
NK005(ca)006:471: dang mnyam par sbyor ba'i dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur
NK005(ca)006:472: ba skabs su babs pa yin /
NK005(ca)006:473: de la dbang gi ngo bo ni /
NK005(ca)006:474: rgyu gnyis rkyen bzhi tshogs pa la brten nas go 'phang gi chos rgyud la 'jog pa'i las kyis /
NK005(ca)006:475: rgyud kyi dri ma byang ba'am nyams smad par byas shing /
NK005(ca)006:476: thar pa'i myu gu mngon du skyes pa'am /
NK005(ca)006:477: skye nges kyi sa bon khyad par can gsos thebs
NK005(ca)006:478: pas lam sgom rung dang 'bras bu thob rung gi
NK005(ca)006:479: nus pa mthu can du smin par byas pa ste
NK005(ca)006:480: / sa bon gsos thebs pa'i cha de sngags kyi sdom pa'ang yin la /
NK005(ca)006:482: nges tshig ni a b+hi shiny+tsa'i sgra las drangs na /
NK005(ca)006:483: mngon par gtor bas na dbang ste /
NK005(ca)006:484: sbyang bya sgo gsum gyi dri ma gtor zhing 'khrud par byed pa'i phyir /
NK005(ca)006:485: yang mngon par blugs pas na dbang ste /
NK005(ca)006:486: lam sgom rung dang 'bras bu thob rung gi nus pa khyad par can rgyud la 'jog pa'i phyir /
NK005(ca)006:487: de ltar yang brtag gnyis las /
NK005(ca)006:488: gtor dang blugs pa zhes bya ba //
NK005(ca)006:489: des na dbang zhes brjod par bya //
NK005(ca)006:495: gsang chen gyi dbang ste bzhi'o //
NK005(ca)006:496: de yang dbang bskur ba ni dkyil 'khor sngon du 'gro ba can yin la /
NK005(ca)006:497: de la'ang rdo rje rtse mo las /
NK005(ca)006:498: sems can shin tu gdul dka' gang //
NK005(ca)006:499: sdom pa 'dzin par mi byed cing //
NK005(ca)006:500: dad dang ldan pa med pa yang //
NK005(ca)006:501: 'jug pa nyid ni dgag mi bya //
NK005(ca)006:502: zhes pas re zhig dbang gi snod du ma gyur pa'i gang zag yin na'ang /
NK005(ca)006:503: dkyil 'khor du bcug pa tsam la 'gal ba med par gsungs mod /
NK005(ca)006:504: dkyil 'khor du ma bcug pa la dbang bskur ba ni nam du'ang mi rung ste /
NK005(ca)006:506: dkyil 'khor ma mthong ba rnams kyi mdun du ma smra zhing zhes gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK005(ca)006:508: kun byas dbang phyug rig pas 'jug /
NK005(ca)006:509: de nas slob ma gzhug par bya //
NK005(ca)006:510: zhes gsungs pa ltar sta gon du gnas pa yan chad song nas /
NK005(ca)006:512: rdo rje slob dpon gyi bya ba dang /
NK005(ca)006:513: rdo rje slob ma'i bya ba gnyis yod pa las /
NK005(ca)006:514: slob dpon gyi bgyi 'os dkyil 'khor bzhengs pa /
NK005(ca)006:516: bdag nyid dkyil 'khor du rig pas 'jug pa rnams chad lhag med par sngon du grub /
NK005(ca)006:517: da khyed rang slob ma rnams kyi ngo skal du gyur pa la /
NK005(ca)006:518: lha dang skal pa mnyam pa'i ched du dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i chos dang /
NK005(ca)006:519: zhugs nas dbang nod pa'i bya ba gnyis las /
NK005(ca)006:520: 'dir 'jug pa'i yan lag khrus dang bgegs bsal ba sngon du song nas /
NK005(ca)006:521: bla ma dang dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo tha mi
NK005(ca)006:522: dad pa la dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i chos rnams
NK005(ca)006:523: zhu ba'i yon du man+dala phul mdzod /
NK005(ca)006:524: ces brjod de slob bus phyag byas man+dala phul te 'dug pa la /
NK005(ca)006:526: zhes pas mig dar dmar po'am dkar pos bcings /
NK005(ca)006:527: sngags des rin po che'i me tog gi phreng ba
NK005(ca)006:528: gtad nas theg pa chen po la rtse gcig tu
NK005(ca)006:531: kye bu khyod ci la dga' bas 'dir 'jug pa yin /
NK005(ca)006:534: bdag skal pa bzang po la dga' bas 'dir 'jug go //
NK005(ca)006:537: de yi khyod la ci zhig bya /
NK005(ca)006:539: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i dngos grub 'dod pa'i phyir ro //
NK005(ca)006:542: me tog dang bcas pa'i thal mo sbyar ba btud de /
NK005(ca)006:543: bde mchog ma dang mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK005(ca)006:544: bdag gi ston pa dga' chen khyod //
NK005(ca)006:545: thugs rjes bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK005(ca)006:546: sangs rgyas sku gsum rang bzhin mchog /
NK005(ca)006:547: slob dpon mgon la bdag skyabs mchi //
NK005(ca)006:548: skal bzang lha mo'i tshogs bcas pa'i //
NK005(ca)006:550: thar pa chen po'i grong mchog tu //
NK005(ca)006:551: mgon pos bdag ni gzhug tu gsol //
NK005(ca)006:552: zhes lan gsum gyis gsol ba btab /
NK005(ca)006:555: rgyal ba kun gyi gnas bzhugs pa'i //
NK005(ca)006:556: dkyil 'khor chen po nyams dga' ba //
NK005(ca)006:558: bdag gis slob ma gzhug par bgyi //
NK005(ca)006:560: gnyis pa nang 'jug la drug las /
NK005(ca)006:562: snying gar kun rdzob byang chub kyi sems zla ba'i
NK005(ca)006:563: dkyil 'khor gyi steng du don dam byang chub kyi
NK005(ca)006:564: sems rdo rjes mtshan par bsam nas /
NK005(ca)006:565: sarba yo ga tsit+ta ut+pa ta ya mi /
NK005(ca)006:566: zhes brjod du bcug pas sems bskyed /
NK005(ca)006:567: yang sngags de nyid brjod cing rdo rje 'dzin pa'i
NK005(ca)006:568: rgyas slob ma'i lag nas 'jus te nang du khrid
NK005(ca)006:569: par mos te yol ba bsal /
NK005(ca)006:570: de yang pad skor lan gsum byas nas g.yon pa'i
NK005(ca)006:571: thal mo kha sbub pa'i steng du g.yas pa'i thal
NK005(ca)006:572: mo bkan mathe'u dang mthe bo bsnol mar spel bas
NK005(ca)006:573: rin po che'i phreng ba bzung ba'o //
NK005(ca)006:575: dkyil 'khor gyi shar sgor gnas pas /
NK005(ca)006:576: thog ma med dus 'khor ba rnams //
NK005(ca)006:577: bdag gis sdig pa'i las gang bgyis //
NK005(ca)006:578: bgyid stsal yi rang dus 'dir bshags //
NK005(ca)006:579: phyin chad mi bgyi'i sdom pa bzung //
NK005(ca)006:580: rgyal ba sras sogs dge rtsa bzhi //
NK005(ca)006:581: 'gro gzhan legs byas gang yin pa //
NK005(ca)006:582: de dag kun la rjes yi rang //
NK005(ca)006:583: byang chub chen por bdag gis bsngo //
NK005(ca)006:584: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun la //
NK005(ca)006:585: bdag ni dus 'dir skyabs su mchi //
NK005(ca)006:586: nyon mongs sdug bsngal bcad pa dang //
NK005(ca)006:587: dge ba'i tshogs mang spel ba'i phyir //
NK005(ca)006:588: byang chub gnyis med sems bskyed nas //
NK005(ca)006:589: 'gro rnams de ring don du gnyer //
NK005(ca)006:590: sangs rgyas gyur nas bdag gis ni //
NK005(ca)006:591: 'gro rnams srid pa'i gnas nas gdon //
NK005(ca)006:593: yang na rgyun bshags dang sdom bzung sta gon gyi skabs bzhin byas na yang legs so //
NK005(ca)006:595: rdo rje me tog gi phreng ba dang bcas pa snying gar bzhag nas //
NK005(ca)006:596: bde gshegs kun gyi khyod nyid ni //
NK005(ca)006:597: de ring byin gyis brlabs pas na //
NK005(ca)006:598: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsang chen 'di //
NK005(ca)006:599: dkyil 'khor dag tu ma bzhugs shing //
NK005(ca)006:600: dad pa med pa'i mi rnams la //
NK005(ca)006:601: nam yang smra bar bya ba min //
NK005(ca)006:602: su ra ta sa ma ya s+t+wam hoh sid+d+hi badz+ra sa ma ya tha su kham /
NK005(ca)006:605: rdo rje sems dpa' deng khyod kyi //
NK005(ca)006:606: snying la yang dag bzhugs mdzad de //
NK005(ca)006:607: gal te tshul 'dir smras na ni //
NK005(ca)006:608: de ma thag tu dral te gshegs //
NK005(ca)006:610: ma h+aa sa ma ya u da ka tha /
NK005(ca)006:611: zhes bzlas pa'i mna' chu blud la /
NK005(ca)006:612: 'di ni khyod kyi dmyal ba'i chu //
NK005(ca)006:613: dam tshig 'das na sreg par byed //
NK005(ca)006:614: dam tshig bsrung na dngos grub ni //
NK005(ca)006:616: +aahh+aum sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h+aum /
NK005(ca)006:618: rdo rje mgo bor bzhag la /
NK005(ca)006:619: de ring phyin chad khyod nyid kyi //
NK005(ca)006:620: rdo rje sems dpa' nga yin pas //
NK005(ca)006:621: gang zhig bsgo ba'i las rnams byos //
NK005(ca)006:622: nga la brnyas par ma byed cig /
NK005(ca)006:623: gal te cung zad brnyas na yang //
NK005(ca)006:624: dus min 'chi zhing dmyal bar ltung //
NK005(ca)006:625: zhes brjod cing dam la bzhag go //
NK005(ca)006:628: rgyal ba kun gyi ye shes thugs //
NK005(ca)006:629: sku dang gsung sprul las mdzad pa //
NK005(ca)006:630: phyag rgya'i cho ga de dag gis //
NK005(ca)006:631: de ring bdag la dbab tu gsol //
NK005(ca)006:633: de nas slob ma'i rkang mthil snying ga mgrin pa
NK005(ca)006:634: spyi bo rnams su yam ram lam kham las 'byung
NK005(ca)006:635: ba bzhi'i dkyil 'khor so so'i sa boon gyis mtshan
NK005(ca)006:636: par bsam nas / sum+b+ha ni sum+b+ha h'u /
NK005(ca)006:637: zhes rta mchog gi sngags drag tu bzlas pas bsrungs la /
NK005(ca)006:638: bdud rtsi lnga dpa' bo 'bru dgus lce thog tu bzhag nas /
NK005(ca)006:639: snying ga'i dbus su dpal rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum mam /
NK005(ca)006:641: rigs drug gi 'khor lo sgyur ba yab yum rnams
NK005(ca)006:642: rjes su chags pa'i bde ba'i 'od zer gyis sangs
NK005(ca)006:643: rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' dpa' bo rnal 'byor
NK005(ca)006:644: ma'i tshogs thams cad rigs drug gi 'khor los sgyur
NK005(ca)006:645: ba'i rnam par spyan drangs te snying gar thim par
NK005(ca)006:646: bsam la / rdzas dud kyis bdug /
NK005(ca)006:647: rdo rje gsor zhing dril bu 'khrol ba dang rol mo sna tshogs pa'i sgra sbyar te /
NK005(ca)006:648: dz+ny+aa na a be sha ya ra ra ra ra ts+aa la ya ts+aa la ya h+aum +aahh+aahdz+hee /
NK005(ca)006:649: zhes brgya rtsa sogs drug tu brjod /
NK005(ca)006:650: de'i tshe lus 'dar zhing 'phar ba dang /
NK005(ca)006:651: drag sngags kyi tshig brjod pa dang /
NK005(ca)006:652: sems la mngon shes 'char ba ste /
NK005(ca)006:653: sku gsung thugs babs pa'i rtags mthong ba nas /
NK005(ca)006:655: ye shes phab pa'i bde ba sbyin pa'i gar dang bcas pas /
NK005(ca)006:656: slob ma dam pa deng phyin chad //
NK005(ca)006:657: phyag rgya'i ye shes rjes bzung bas //
NK005(ca)006:658: rnam par snang mdzad mchog bzhin du //
NK005(ca)006:659: sangs rgyas kun gyi bdag nyid 'grub //
NK005(ca)006:660: ces che ba'i yon tan brjod /
NK005(ca)006:662: mig dar dang bcas pas dkyil 'khor gyi steng gi
NK005(ca)006:663: nam mkhar bltar bcug ste snang ba dris nas kha
NK005(ca)006:664: dog gang mthong ba de dang mthun pa'i phrin las
NK005(ca)006:666: de nas bden pas byin gyis brlab pa'i phyir dril bu 'khrol bzhin du /
NK005(ca)006:668: slob ma mchog 'di gzhug par bgyi //
NK005(ca)006:669: rigs kyi lha yi bye brag dang //
NK005(ca)006:670: bsod nams gang yin de bzhin shog /
NK005(ca)006:671: ces brjod nas sngar bzung ba'i me tog gi phreng ba /
NK005(ca)006:672: pra t+aits+tsha badz+ra hoh zhes dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo la 'bul bas /
NK005(ca)006:673: lha gang la babs pa de yi dam du sbyin zhing /
NK005(ca)006:674: de yang gtso bo'i sku'i stod smad la sogs pa'i dbye bas dngos grub mchog la sogs pa dang /
NK005(ca)006:676: ra ba las 'das na lan gsum bskyar zhing /
NK005(ca)006:677: de nas kyang phyir lhung na bum chus shis par byas nas gtong bar bshad do //
NK005(ca)006:678: de nas phreng ba de slob ma'i spyi bor 'ching zhing /
NK005(ca)006:679: stobs ldan sems dpa'i rgyal po che //
NK005(ca)006:680: phreng ba 'di nas ldan par gyis //
NK005(ca)006:681: rat+na m+aa le a b+hi shiny+tsa tram /
NK005(ca)006:684: gyis basngagasa pa'i gser gyi thur ma pra yig gis mtshan ma thogs nas //
NK005(ca)006:685: rdo rje sems dpa' deng khyod kyi //
NK005(ca)006:686: mig 'byed par ni brtson par mdzad //
NK005(ca)006:687: sgrib g.yogs ling thog kun bsal bas //
NK005(ca)006:688: rdo rje'i mig ni bla na med //
NK005(ca)006:689: badz+ra tsak+shu dz+ny+aa na pra be sha ya phata /
NK005(ca)006:690: ces gdong g.yogs bsal nas dkyil 'khor mtshon par byas te /
NK005(ca)006:691: legs par ltos shig sems dpa' che //
NK005(ca)006:692: thar pa chen po'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK005(ca)006:693: me tog gang la lhung ba ni //
NK005(ca)006:694: de nyid khyod kyi rigs kyi lha //
NK005(ca)006:695: zhes rta mgrin 'phang mtho nas gtso bo'i mthar thug
NK005(ca)006:696: pa'i bar gyi lha rnams so so'i mtshan brjod pas
NK005(ca)006:698: bza' btung la sogs pa'i mchod pa'i tshogs kyis lha
NK005(ca)006:699: dang slob dpon dang rnal 'byor pa rnams mnyes par
NK005(ca)006:701: bu khyod dad pas rab gus skyed //
NK005(ca)006:703: sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK005(ca)006:705: 'gro ba phun sum tshogs kun dang //
NK005(ca)006:706: dngos grub thams cad mngon du 'gyur //
NK005(ca)006:707: dam tshig ting 'dzin rjes chags dang //
NK005(ca)006:708: gsang sngags snying po 'dzin par gyis //
NK005(ca)006:710: de dag ni dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i cho ga'o //
NK005(ca)006:711: gnyis pa zhugs pa la dbang bskur ba ni /
NK005(ca)006:715: gsang chen gyi dbang bskur ba dang bzhi las /
NK005(ca)006:716: dang po la slob ma'i dang /
NK005(ca)006:718: dang po la sngon du bya ba dang /
NK005(ca)006:720: rjes gdams ngag brjod pa gsum las /
NK005(ca)006:722: slob mas ji ltar 'byor ba'i yon dang man+dala phul nas thal mo sbyar te /
NK005(ca)006:723: rgyal ba kun gyi gsang ba'i lam //
NK005(ca)006:724: 'gro ba skyob pa'i gzi brjid can //
NK005(ca)006:726: yon tan thams cad 'byung ba'i gnas //
NK005(ca)006:727: de ring dbang bskur gnang ba yi //
NK005(ca)006:728: dus la babs pa'i 'os pa lags //
NK005(ca)006:729: dpa' bo chen po mi ldog pa'i //
NK005(ca)006:730: dbang bskur rim bzhin bdag la stsol //
NK005(ca)006:731: rigs pa chen po'i las bsgrubs nas //
NK005(ca)006:732: dngos grub mchog rnams shes pa dang //
NK005(ca)006:733: sems can kun gyi don gyi phyir //
NK005(ca)006:734: bdag gis rdo rje slob dpon bzung //
NK005(ca)006:736: de nas dkyil 'khor gyi shar sgo las khru do
NK005(ca)006:737: tsam gyis chong pa'i sar dbang stegs rtsa ba'i dkyil
NK005(ca)006:738: 'khor gyi lte ba dang mnyam pa brtsigs pa'am /
NK005(ca)006:739: ba byung dang dri bzang gis byugs pa la pad+ma
NK005(ca)006:740: 'dab brgyad phyi rol gru bzhi sgo dang bcas pa
NK005(ca)006:741: bris pa'i dbus su seng khri pad+ma'i gdan la slob
NK005(ca)006:742: ma gus pa'i sems kyi gnas pa la /
NK005(ca)006:744: me tog gi phreng ba dang /
NK005(ca)006:746: gos sna tshogs kyis mdzes shing mchod pa'i tshogs kyis bskor bar gyur pa la /
NK005(ca)006:750: sarba pa p+aam da ha na badz+ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK005(ca)006:751: zhes yungs kar gyis bskor nas me nang du dor /
NK005(ca)006:752: sarba s+aam sho d+ha ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK005(ca)006:753: zhes ku sha dang bcas pa'i chus gtor zhing byabs la /
NK005(ca)006:754: byur dang skal ba ngan pa dang bkra mi shis pa thams cad sh+aan+tim ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK005(ca)006:755: zhes yungs kar gyi bzed zhal phyir dor zhing rol mo'i sgra sbyar /
NK005(ca)006:756: de nas las bum gyi chus bsangs shing rta mchog gi sngags lan gsum bzlas pas bsrungs /
NK005(ca)006:757: slar yang bdud rtsi gtor nas /
NK005(ca)006:760: swa b+h+aa wa'i sngags brjod de /
NK005(ca)006:761: chos nyid rnam par dag pa'i rang bzhin las slob
NK005(ca)006:762: bu rdo rje sems dpa' yum dang bcas pa'i gzugs
NK005(ca)006:764: gnyis pa dngos gzhi'i dbang bskur ba la chu /
NK005(ca)006:770: mchod dbyangs rol mo'i sgra dang bcas pas bum chu dung zhal du blangs te //
NK005(ca)006:771: phun sum tshogs pa mnga' ba gser gyi ro bo 'dra //
NK005(ca)006:772: 'jig rten gsum gyi mgon po dri ma gsum spangs pa //
NK005(ca)006:773: sangs rgyas pad+ma rgyas pa'i 'dab 'dra'i spyan mnga' ba //
NK005(ca)006:774: bkra shis des ni skye dgu rnams la zhi byed dang po'o //
NK005(ca)006:775: de yis nye bar bstan pa'i mchog rab mi g.yo ba //
NK005(ca)006:776: 'jig rten gsum na grags shing lha dang mis mchod pa //
NK005(ca)006:777: chos kyi dam pa skye dgu rnams la zhi byed pa //
NK005(ca)006:778: de ni 'jig rten dge ba'i bkra shis gnyis pa'o //
NK005(ca)006:779: dge 'dun dam pa'i chos ldan thos pa bkra shis phyug /
NK005(ca)006:780: mi dang lha dang lha ma yin gyis mchod pa'i gnas //
NK005(ca)006:781: tshogs kyi mchog rab ngo tshas shes dang dpal gyi gzhi //
NK005(ca)006:782: de ni 'jig rten dge ba'i bkra shis gsum pa'o //
NK005(ca)006:783: zhes bkra shis kyi glu blang ba sngon du 'gro bas /
NK005(ca)006:784: til gyi gang bu bzhin gang ba'i //
NK005(ca)006:785: rgyal ba'i bum pa bzung nas ni //
NK005(ca)006:786: 'di nyid du ni blugs mdzad pas //
NK005(ca)006:787: bag chags ma lus dag gyur cig /
NK005(ca)006:788: ces phyi bum gyis khrus bya'o //
NK005(ca)006:789: de nas slob dpon gyi thugs ka nas 'od zer
NK005(ca)006:790: lcags kyu lta bu 'phros pas dbang gi lha rigs
NK005(ca)006:791: drug gi dkyil 'khor sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems
NK005(ca)006:792: dpa' dpa' bo dang rnal 'byor ma'i tshogs kyis bskor
NK005(ca)006:793: ba badz+ra sa ma ya dzahs spyan drangs /
NK005(ca)006:794: mdun gyi nam mkhar zla ba'i dkyil 'khor la bzhugs par bsam la /
NK005(ca)006:795: ma h+aa sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK005(ca)006:796: zhes lan gnyis kyis chu gnyis dang //
NK005(ca)006:797: rdo rje sems dpa' bsdus pa na //
NK005(ca)006:798: rdo rjee rin chen bla na med //
NK005(ca)006:799: rdo rje chos ni glur blangs pas //
NK005(ca)006:800: rdo rje las kun byed par 'gyur //
NK005(ca)006:804: badz+ra +aa lo ke h+r+aih badz+ra gan+d+he h+aam /
NK005(ca)006:806: badz+ra a ha ra h+r+aih na mahsarba ta th+aa ga
NK005(ca)006:807: ta b+h+yo a lang+ka ra pa na bee h+aum s+w+aa
NK005(ca)006:808: h+aa / b+h+yo d+h+yam rat+na me g+ha s+pha ra na h+aum /
NK005(ca)006:810: de nas slob ma rdo rje sems dpa' nyid du
NK005(ca)006:811: gnas pa las dbang rdzas rnams so sor bskyed par
NK005(ca)006:812: bya ste / bum pa gzhan gyi chu rnams gtso bum du bsdus /
NK005(ca)006:813: ma h+aa su sha badz+ra sat+wa a /
NK005(ca)006:814: dzahh+aum bam hoh su ra ta s+t+wam /
NK005(ca)006:816: he ru ka badz+ra sa ma ya h+r+aihsarba dush+tana sa ma ya mu dra pra b+hany+dza ka h+aum phata /
NK005(ca)006:817: swa b+h+aa wa shud+d+ha sarba d+har+m+aa nirte shwa ra h+r+aihdzah sid+d+han+tu /
NK005(ca)006:819: sid+d+h+ya ma h+aa badz+ra rat+na ba ba ta ta tram /
NK005(ca)006:821: zhes 'khor los sgyur ba drug gi sngags brjod /
NK005(ca)006:823: dbang rdzas bum pa mi dmigs te stong pa nyid du gyur /
NK005(ca)006:824: stong pa'i ngang las h+r+aihls he ru ka mthing nag
NK005(ca)006:825: zhal gcig phyag bzhi pa g.yas gnyis rdo rje dang
NK005(ca)006:826: dung khrag / g.yon gnyis gshor thong dang zhags pa 'dzin pa /
NK005(ca)006:827: yum kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai ma sngo skya thod khrag
NK005(ca)006:828: dang ba dan rtse gsum pa'i phyag rgya can dang
NK005(ca)006:829: mnyam par sbyor ba'i dpral bar /
NK005(ca)006:831: h+aum las 'od zer 'phros sangs rgyas thams cad he
NK005(ca)006:832: ru ka'i rnam par badz+ra sa m+aa dzah dzahh+aum bam
NK005(ca)006:833: hoh gnyis su med par gyur /
NK005(ca)006:834: yab yum snyoms par zhugs te zhu ba las byang chub sems kyi bum chur gyur /
NK005(ca)006:835: mdun bskyed kyi dkyil 'khor dang dbang lha yab yum
NK005(ca)006:836: snyoms par zhugs pa'i byang chub sems kyi chu rgyun
NK005(ca)006:837: bum chu dang 'dres pas gang ba'i bum pa 'dzin
NK005(ca)006:838: pa'i bzang mo sogs 'khor lo'i bdag mo rnams dang
NK005(ca)006:839: bde mchog ma sogs rigs kyi lha mo rnams kyi
NK005(ca)006:840: bkra shis kyi glu dbyangs dang bcas pas phyogs bzhi
NK005(ca)006:841: nas bkru zhing dbang bskur bas bsam la /
NK005(ca)006:842: bkra shis gang zhig sems can kun gyi snying la gnas //
NK005(ca)006:843: kun gyi bdag nyid rigs kun gyi ni bdag po mchog /
NK005(ca)006:844: ma lus sems can bskyed mdzad bde ba chen po ste //
NK005(ca)006:845: des ni deng khyod dbang bskur mchog la bkra shis shog /
NK005(ca)006:846: ces bkra shis brjod pa sngon du 'gro bas //
NK005(ca)006:847: lha yi chu ni rnam dag pa //
NK005(ca)006:848: rdo rje gsang gsum gnas las byung //
NK005(ca)006:849: rig pa'i lha mo'i tshogs ldan pa'i //
NK005(ca)006:850: rang bzhin gcig tu gyur pa yin //
NK005(ca)006:853: 'khor los sgyur ba drug gi snying po tshang ba'am /
NK005(ca)006:854: ma h+aa su sha badz+ra sat+wa ah dzahh+aum bam hoh zhes rdor sems kyi snying po dang /
NK005(ca)006:855: h+aum hi h+r+ai tram h+aam h+aam h+aam h+aam /
NK005(ca)006:858: zhes btags pas chu dbang bskur /
NK005(ca)006:859: de ltar me long lta bu'i ye shes kyi rang
NK005(ca)006:860: bzhin he ru kar mtshon pas dbang bskur bas chos
NK005(ca)006:861: thams cad kyi rang bzhin he ru kar rtogs par
NK005(ca)006:862: bya'o // zhes go bar brda sprad do //
NK005(ca)006:864: rigs drug so so'i dbu rgyan rigs kyi dbye bas rnam pa mi 'dra bar bshad pa las /
NK005(ca)006:865: rdo rje sems dpa'i rigs la dbu rgyan rin po
NK005(ca)006:866: che sogs la byas pa rtse mo lnga pa rin
NK005(ca)006:867: po che'i khang bu sgo can gyi dbus na sangs
NK005(ca)006:868: rgyas lnga bzhugs pa dar dkar dmar gyi khebs dang
NK005(ca)006:869: bcas pa / sangs rgyas drug mtshon pa'i thod pa
NK005(ca)006:870: drug gi phreng ba can gtsug gi nor bu rdo
NK005(ca)006:873: dbu rgyan mi dmigs te stong pa'i ngang las t+r+aam las rdo rje nyi ma zhal bzhi ser ba /
NK005(ca)006:874: phyag bzhi'i dang po gnyis mda' dang gzhu /
NK005(ca)006:875: 'og ma gnyis ral gri dang nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor dang rdo rje mtshan pa'i pad+ma bsnams pa /
NK005(ca)006:876: yum m+aa ma k+ai sngon mo rin po che dang
NK005(ca)006:877: thod pa 'dzin pa dang mnyam par sbyor ba'i dpral
NK005(ca)006:878: bar / mgrin par +aah thugs kar h+aum /
NK005(ca)006:879: h+aum las 'od zer 'phros sangs rgyas thams cad rdo
NK005(ca)006:880: rje nyi ma'i rnam par badz+ra sa ma dzah dzahh+aum
NK005(ca)006:881: bam hoh gnyis su med par gyur /
NK005(ca)006:882: yab yum snyoms par zhugs te zhu ba las dbu
NK005(ca)006:883: rgyan rgyal ba rigs lnga'i khang bu can thod pa'i
NK005(ca)006:884: phreng ba dar dpyangs dang bcas par gyur //
NK005(ca)006:885: sangs rgyas kun gyis basngagasa pa yi //
NK005(ca)006:886: rin chen las byung dbu rgyan che //
NK005(ca)006:887: thor tshugs cod pan gyis brgyan pa'i //
NK005(ca)006:888: dar dpyangs dbu rgyan sbyin par bya //
NK005(ca)006:890: badz+ra a ra li hoh a b+hi shiny+tsa tram /
NK005(ca)006:891: zhes byin nas thod pa'i mtshan ma drug dang bcas pa'i dar dpyangs bcings te //
NK005(ca)006:892: sangs rgyas kun gyi ye shes brtags //
NK005(ca)006:893: thod pa'i phreng ba'i dbu rgyan gyis //
NK005(ca)006:894: rdo rje'i sems dpa' bdag sngon bskyed //
NK005(ca)006:895: rig pa'i ye shes mtshan ma'i rtags //
NK005(ca)006:896: badz+ra ka p+aa la a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK005(ca)006:897: de ltar mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes kyi rang
NK005(ca)006:898: bzhin rdo rje nyi mar mtshon pa'i dbang bskur bas
NK005(ca)006:899: / chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin rdo rje nyi mar rtogs par bya'o //
NK005(ca)006:901: rdo rje rtse lnga pa sbyangs nas /
NK005(ca)006:902: rdo rje mi dmigs te stong pa'i gang las h+r+aihls
NK005(ca)006:903: pad+ma gar gyi dbang phyug dmar la dkar ba'i mdangs
NK005(ca)006:904: can zhal cig phyag bzhi'i dang po gnyis chos 'chad
NK005(ca)006:905: kyis pad+ma'i sdong bu gnyis dang /
NK005(ca)006:906: 'og ma gnyis kyis mda' gzhu 'dzin pa /
NK005(ca)006:907: yum gos dkar mo thod khrag 'dzin pa dang mnyam par sbyor ba'i dpral bar /
NK005(ca)006:909: h+aum las 'od zer 'phros sangs rgyas thams cad pad+ma
NK005(ca)006:910: gar gyi dbang phyug gi rnam par badz+ra sa m+aa
NK005(ca)006:911: dzah dzahh+aum bam hoh gnyis su med par gyur /
NK005(ca)006:912: yab yum snyoms par zhugs te zhu ba las rdo rjer gyur //
NK005(ca)006:913: 'di ni sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK005(ca)006:914: rdo rje gsang ba chen po'i don //
NK005(ca)006:915: de ring khyod la dbang bskur te //
NK005(ca)006:916: rab tu grub phyir gzung bar gyis //
NK005(ca)006:917: badz+ra sat+wa s+t+wam a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK005(ca)006:918: zhes snying gar gtugs nas slar yang lag g.yas su
NK005(ca)006:919: gtad nas des lan gsum gsor te snying gar bzung
NK005(ca)006:920: nas // thog mtha' med pa'i sems dpa' ni //
NK005(ca)006:921: rdo rje sems dpa' dga' ba che //
NK005(ca)006:922: kun tu bzang po kun bdag nyid //
NK005(ca)006:923: rdo rje snyems tshul bdag po'i bdag /
NK005(ca)006:924: ces rdo rje de kho na nyid bsam /
NK005(ca)006:925: de ltar so sor rtog pa'i ye shes kyi rang
NK005(ca)006:926: bzhin pad+ma gar dbang du mtshon pa'i dbang bskur bas
NK005(ca)006:927: chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin pad+ma gar dbang du
NK005(ca)006:928: rtogs par bya'o // bzhi pa ni /
NK005(ca)006:930: dril bu mi dmigs te stong pa'i ngang las h+aam
NK005(ca)006:931: las rdo rje rta mchog ljang gu khro bo zhal
NK005(ca)006:934: phyag bzhi dang po gnyis sna tshogs rdo rje dang sna tshogs pad+ma /
NK005(ca)006:935: 'og ma gnyis ba dan gsum pa dang ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK005(ca)006:936: yum dam tshig sgrol ma ljang gu gri thod 'dzin pa dang mnyam par sbyor ba'i dpral bar /
NK005(ca)006:938: h+aum las 'od zer 'phros sangs rgyas thams cad rdo
NK005(ca)006:939: rje rta mchog gi rnam par badz+ra sa m+aa dzah
NK005(ca)006:940: dzahh+aum bam hoh gnyis su med par gyur /
NK005(ca)006:941: yab yum snyoms par zhugs te zhu ba las dril bur gyur /
NK005(ca)006:943: shes rab dbyings kyi rjes 'gror bshad //
NK005(ca)006:944: khyod kyis rtag tu bzung bar bya //
NK005(ca)006:945: byang chub mchog tu rgyal ba bzhed //
NK005(ca)006:946: a d+hi pa ti s+t+wam a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK005(ca)006:947: zhes dkrol zhing lag g.yon du gtad /
NK005(ca)006:948: des dkrol nas dkur bzung ba la /
NK005(ca)006:949: srid pa ngo bo nyid kyis dag /
NK005(ca)006:950: ngo bo nyid kyi srid bral byas //
NK005(ca)006:951: rang bzhin dag pa'i sems can rnams //
NK005(ca)006:952: dam pa'i srid pa byed par 'gyur //
NK005(ca)006:953: zhes dril bu'i de kho na nyid bzung /
NK005(ca)006:954: de ltar bya ba grub pa'i ye shes kyi rang
NK005(ca)006:955: bzhin rta mchog tu mtshon pa'i dbang bskur bas chos
NK005(ca)006:956: thams cad kyi rang bzhin rta mchog tu rtogs par
NK005(ca)006:958: rdor dril mi dmigs te stong pa'i ngang las las
NK005(ca)006:959: rnam par snang mdzad dkar po dkar ser dmar ba'i
NK005(ca)006:960: zhal bzhi pa / phyag bzhi'i dang po gnyis kyis chos gos gsol ba'i grwa dang lhung bzed /
NK005(ca)006:961: 'og ma gnyis kyi mkhar gsil dang glegs bam 'dzin pa /
NK005(ca)006:962: yum sangs rgyas spyan ma dkar mo 'khor lo dang
NK005(ca)006:963: thod pa 'dzin pa dang mnyam par sbyor ba'i dpral
NK005(ca)006:964: par / mgrin par +aah thugs kar h+aum /
NK005(ca)006:965: h+aum las 'od zer 'phros sangs rgyas thams cad rnam
NK005(ca)006:966: par snang mdzad kyi rnam par badz+ra sa m+aa dzah
NK005(ca)006:967: dzahh+aum bam ho / gnyis su med par gyur /
NK005(ca)006:968: yab yum snyoms par zhugs te zhu ba las rdo rje dril bur gyur /
NK005(ca)006:969: thabs shes sbyor ba ste 'khyud rgyas rdor dril spyi bor bzung la //
NK005(ca)006:970: gang phyir chos rnams rnam dag pas //
NK005(ca)006:971: sangs rgyas ye shes rang bzhin nyid //
NK005(ca)006:972: dbang po'i spyod yul gang dag gang //
NK005(ca)006:973: bde mchog sgyu ma'i dkyil 'khor nyid //
NK005(ca)006:974: kyee dpal che ge mo a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK005(ca)006:975: badz+ra n+aa ma a b+hi she ka ta ya hoh zhes brjod cing /
NK005(ca)006:977: de ltar chos kyi dbyings shin tu rnam par dag
NK005(ca)006:978: pa'i rang bzhin rnam par snang mdzad du mtshon pa'i
NK005(ca)006:979: dbang bskur bas / chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin rnam par snang mdzad du rtogs par bya'o //
NK005(ca)006:981: de ltar dbang thob pa'i phan yon dang nyes dmigs bsgrags te /
NK005(ca)006:982: sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK005(ca)006:983: mkha' 'gro ma yi tshig gis kyang //
NK005(ca)006:984: rgyas mi thebs shing mi rmongs te //
NK005(ca)006:985: de la gnod par mi 'gyur ro //
NK005(ca)006:987: sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK005(ca)006:988: sdom pa nyams par khyod byed na //
NK005(ca)006:989: ji snyed sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK005(ca)006:990: byang chub sems dpa' rdo rje 'dzin //
NK005(ca)006:991: lha rnams dang ni mi dag dang //
NK005(ca)006:992: de bzhin rnal 'byor sgrub pa po //
NK005(ca)006:993: de dag la ni snying bsrings nas //
NK005(ca)006:995: sems can khams ni ma lus don //
NK005(ca)006:996: srid pa shin tu dag bya'i phyir //
NK005(ca)006:997: mi 'gog chos nyid sbyor ba yis //
NK005(ca)006:998: rtag pa nyid du bsgrub par bya //
NK005(ca)006:999: rang gi ngo bo rnams spangs shing //
NK005(ca)006:1000: dka' thub kyis ni gzir mi bya //
NK005(ca)006:1001: ci bde bar ni bde bar spyad //
NK005(ca)006:1002: 'di ni phyi dus sangs rgyas yin //
NK005(ca)006:1003: rnal 'byor longs spyod thams cad la //
NK005(ca)006:1004: cis kyang mi 'jigs dga' bar gyis //
NK005(ca)006:1005: mi 'jigs khyod la sdig pa med //
NK005(ca)006:1007: zhes brjod cing sku gsung thugs kyi dam tshig gsum rgyas par bstan no //
NK005(ca)006:1008: gnyis pa rdo rje slob dpon gyi dbang la /
NK005(ca)006:1013: gdams ngag bstan pa dang lnga'o //
NK005(ca)006:1014: dang po la gsol gdab brtul zhugs sbyin pa mchod pa dang gsum gyi /
NK005(ca)006:1016: rdo rje slob dpon du bya zhing gzhan gyi don bsgrub par 'dod pas man+dala phul te /
NK005(ca)006:1017: mgon khyod thugs rje'i bka' drin gyis //
NK005(ca)006:1018: dkyil 'khor slob dpon dbang bskur sogs //
NK005(ca)006:1019: bdag gzhan don gyi bya ba rnams //
NK005(ca)006:1020: 'grub byed dbang bskur bdag la stsol //
NK005(ca)006:1023: slob ma rdo rje slob dpon mchog tu mnga' gsol
NK005(ca)006:1024: ba'i phyir dkyil 'khor dbus su dbang stegs kyi steng
NK005(ca)006:1025: du dpal rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum gyi rnam
NK005(ca)006:1026: pas 'khod pa'i phyogs thams cad mchod pa'i tshogs kyis
NK005(ca)006:1028: gtso bo yab yum gyi bdag nyid rdo rje dang dril bu gtad nas /
NK005(ca)006:1029: rdo rje dril bu phyag rgya che //
NK005(ca)006:1030: bzung zhing yang dag bzung bar gyis //
NK005(ca)006:1031: de ring rdo rje slob dpon che //
NK005(ca)006:1032: slob ma'i tshogs rnams bsdu bar gyis //
NK005(ca)006:1034: 'di ni sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK005(ca)006:1035: rdo rje sems dpa'i phyag na gnas //
NK005(ca)006:1036: khyod kyis rtag tu bzung bar bya //
NK005(ca)006:1037: phyag na rdo rje'i brtul zhugs brtan //
NK005(ca)006:1039: sarba ta th+aa ga ta badz+ra sa ma ya tish+tha
NK005(ca)006:1040: i sha s+t+wam d+ha ra ya mi hi hi hi
NK005(ca)006:1041: hi h+aum / zhes de kho na nyid kyis bzung ngo //
NK005(ca)006:1042: 'di de sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK005(ca)006:1043: shes rab dbyings kyi rjes 'gror bshad //
NK005(ca)006:1044: khyod kyis kyang ni rtag tu bcing //
NK005(ca)006:1045: byang chub mchog tu rgyal ba bzhed //
NK005(ca)006:1049: de nas phyag rgya dang mnyam par sbyor ba las
NK005(ca)006:1050: byung ba'i bde ba nyams su myong bar byas te
NK005(ca)006:1051: / yid kyi lus ni brtan pa nyid //
NK005(ca)006:1052: phyag rgya'i dam tshig ces byar brjod //
NK005(ca)006:1053: lus kun brtan byed gang zhig ni //
NK005(ca)006:1054: phyag rgyar rab tu grags pa yin //
NK005(ca)006:1055: ma h+aa k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum /
NK005(ca)006:1056: zhes phyag rgya'i dam tshig ste /
NK005(ca)006:1057: dam tshig gsum dang ldan pa'i slob ma rdo rje
NK005(ca)006:1058: slob dpon gyi gnas thob pa la dbang lha thams
NK005(ca)006:1059: cad ye shes sems dpa'i ngo bor bstim nas bkra
NK005(ca)006:1060: shis kyi glu dbyangs sngon du 'gro bas rol mo'i
NK005(ca)006:1062: su pra tish+tha badz+ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK005(ca)006:1063: zhes me tog dor zhing brtan par bya'o //
NK005(ca)006:1065: slob dpon rdo rje sems dpa'i nga rgyal gyi snyems
NK005(ca)006:1066: dang bcas pas me tog gi phreng ba sogs mchod
NK005(ca)006:1068: deng nas brtsams te rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK005(ca)006:1069: sras dang bcas pa rnam rol zhing //
NK005(ca)006:1070: rdo rje snyems pa'i rnal 'byor gyis //
NK005(ca)006:1071: dga' ston bde ba'i mchod par gyis //
NK005(ca)006:1073: sgeg dang bcas pas phreng ba 'phang //
NK005(ca)006:1074: sangs rgyas thams cad mchod par bya //
NK005(ca)006:1075: bcom ldan kun tu mi 'bral te //
NK005(ca)006:1076: phreng ba de yi rgyan yin no //
NK005(ca)006:1078: lus can rnams la dam chos kyi //
NK005(ca)006:1079: glu ni khyod kyis blang bar bya //
NK005(ca)006:1080: de yis bde gshegs dngos grub ni //
NK005(ca)006:1081: myur du bde bar myong bar 'gyur //
NK005(ca)006:1083: de nyid thal mo gar gyis ni //
NK005(ca)006:1084: sangs rgyas thams cad mchod par byos //
NK005(ca)006:1085: sangs rgyas 'dul ba'i phrin las kyis //
NK005(ca)006:1086: gar mkhan tshul bzhin bsgyur bar gyis //
NK005(ca)006:1088: rdzogs sangs rgyas la spos phul bas //
NK005(ca)006:1089: brtul zhugs bzang po legs par tshim //
NK005(ca)006:1090: lus can bde gshegs cha 'dra bar //
NK005(ca)006:1091: ye shes can gyis mchod par gyis //
NK005(ca)006:1093: sangs rgyas rnams la me tog gtor //
NK005(ca)006:1094: byang chub yan lag tshogs gyur pas //
NK005(ca)006:1095: mtshan dang dpe byad ldan pa yi //
NK005(ca)006:1096: bde gshegs sku ni thob par 'gyur //
NK005(ca)006:1099: rdo rje chos gang 'dra ba ru //
NK005(ca)006:1100: sems can ma rig mun 'thom pa'i //
NK005(ca)006:1101: ye shes snang ba gsal bar gyis //
NK005(ca)006:1103: rgyal ba rnams la dri phul bas //
NK005(ca)006:1104: tshul khrims ting 'dzin shes rab dang //
NK005(ca)006:1105: rnam grol ye shes mthong ba yi //
NK005(ca)006:1106: byang chub lus can rnams la bgos //
NK005(ca)006:1108: de ltar so so'i gar dang bcas pas mchod par bya'o //
NK005(ca)006:1109: 'di dag la gzhan du mchod pa'i rjes gnang zer
NK005(ca)006:1110: yang 'dir brtul zhugs kyi mtha' rgyas su bshad cing
NK005(ca)006:1111: / h+aum mdzad kyi dbang chog tu mchod pa'i sngags
NK005(ca)006:1112: tshig ma gsungs pas ma byas kyang chog par mngon
NK005(ca)006:1113: / no // gnyis pa rjes gnang la drug gi dang po ni /
NK005(ca)006:1114: bdag gzhan don grub las kyi tshogs //
NK005(ca)006:1115: thun mong 'bring po mchog gyur pa //
NK005(ca)006:1116: zhi rgyas dbang dang dgug pa dang //
NK005(ca)006:1117: sdang gnod rengs pa'i las kun dang //
NK005(ca)006:1118: dbye rmongs bskrad pa'i cho ga rnams //
NK005(ca)006:1119: thogs pa med par sgrub par gyis //
NK005(ca)006:1120: ral gri mig sman sa 'og dang //
NK005(ca)006:1122: gser 'gyur ril bu nyi zla gsungs //
NK005(ca)006:1123: char dbabs la sogs las kyi tshogs //
NK005(ca)006:1124: rnam shes sgrub dang ye shes sgrub //
NK005(ca)006:1125: phyag rgya shes pa'i dngos grub dang //
NK005(ca)006:1126: thams cad 'grub cing grol ba las //
NK005(ca)006:1127: de nyid yang dag sbyor bar gyis //
NK005(ca)006:1128: rgyal ba kun gyi gnas 'jug cing //
NK005(ca)006:1129: sku gsung thugs mchog yon tan rgyas //
NK005(ca)006:1130: phrin las bdag gzhan gnas sbyor ba'i //
NK005(ca)006:1131: mkha' 'gro sgyu ma'i dngos grub sgrubs //
NK005(ca)006:1132: zhes thun mong dang mchog gi dngos grub sgrub pa'i rjes su gnang bar bya'o //
NK005(ca)006:1134: mig sman gser gyi thur mas blang ba mig la
NK005(ca)006:1135: byugs tshul byas pas de'i rab rib bsal bar bsam
NK005(ca)006:1136: zhing / ji ltar mig mkhan rgyal po yis //
NK005(ca)006:1137: 'jig rten ling thog bsal ba ltar //
NK005(ca)006:1138: bu khyod kyi ni mi shes pa'i //
NK005(ca)006:1139: rab rib rgyal ba rnams kyis bsal //
NK005(ca)006:1140: badz+ra nee t+r+aa ba ha ra pa ta lim h+r+aih zhes mig phyes te me long bstan nas /
NK005(ca)006:1141: chos rnams gzugs brnyan lta bu ste //
NK005(ca)006:1142: gsal zhing dwangs la rnyog pa med //
NK005(ca)006:1143: gzung 'dzin rnam bral brjod du med //
NK005(ca)006:1144: rgyu dang las las kun tu 'byung //
NK005(ca)006:1145: rang bzhin med cing bdag med pa //
NK005(ca)006:1146: de ltar chos rnams shes gyis la //
NK005(ca)006:1147: sems can don ni mnyam med byos //
NK005(ca)006:1148: de ni sangs rgyas rigs su skyes //
NK005(ca)006:1149: zhes pas kun rdzob kyi chos thams cad gzugs brnyan
NK005(ca)006:1150: dang sgyu ma lta bur snang ba la spyod pa'i
NK005(ca)006:1151: rjes gnang ngo // gsum pa ni /
NK005(ca)006:1152: dril bu 'khrol ba'i sgras mtshon par /
NK005(ca)006:1153: thams cad nam mkha'i mtshan nyid de //
NK005(ca)006:1154: nam mkha' la ni mtshan nyid med //
NK005(ca)006:1155: nam mkha' dag dang mnyam sbyor bas //
NK005(ca)006:1156: kun mchog mnyam pa nyid du gsal //
NK005(ca)006:1159: rdo rje sems dpa' me long bzhin //
NK005(ca)006:1160: dag cing gsal la rnyog pa med //
NK005(ca)006:1161: bu khyod kyi ni snying la bzhugs //
NK005(ca)006:1162: rdo rje sems dpa' rang nyid gtso //
NK005(ca)006:1163: zhes brjod pas don dam pa dang yi dam gyi lha ji ltar gnas pa'i mtshan nyid bstan pa'o //
NK005(ca)006:1165: yang lha mo pad+ma 'dzin mas byin gyis brlab par bshad pa bzhin /
NK005(ca)006:1166: dzahbadz+ra d+aish+ta sa ma ke phata /
NK005(ca)006:1167: ces mda' gzhu sbyin te des kyang phyogs bzhi dang
NK005(ca)006:1168: steng 'og tu 'phen pa'i tshul bya zhing sems can
NK005(ca)006:1169: la chags pa'i rjes gnang ngo //
NK005(ca)006:1171: de nas rkang 'og tu 'khor lo bzhag /
NK005(ca)006:1172: lag g.yas su rgyud kyi glegs bam dang g.yon du 'bud dung byin te bsgrags par bya zhing //
NK005(ca)006:1173: pha rol phyin drug las rnams kyis //
NK005(ca)006:1174: sems can don kun rab sbyor zhing //
NK005(ca)006:1176: chos kyi 'khor lo chen po bskor //
NK005(ca)006:1177: the tshom rtog tshogs gcod mdzad pa'i //
NK005(ca)006:1178: chos kyi dung gi sgra sgrogs shing //
NK005(ca)006:1179: gsang sngags gsang chen snying po'i don //
NK005(ca)006:1180: snod ldan kun la rab tu shod //
NK005(ca)006:1181: des ni rgyal ba thams cad la //
NK005(ca)006:1182: phan thogs drin du gzo zhes bya //
NK005(ca)006:1184: khyod la rtag tu bsrung bar mdzad //
NK005(ca)006:1185: ces pas rdo rje slob dpon gyi bya ba bsgrub pa la rjes su gnang ba'o //
NK005(ca)006:1187: de nas rigs kyi 'khor lo lnga bskor bar gnang ba sbyin pa ni /
NK005(ca)006:1188: mdor na 'jig rten khams rnams su //
NK005(ca)006:1189: sems can kun gyi don gyi phyir //
NK005(ca)006:1190: ji ltar 'dul ba sna tshogs kyis //
NK005(ca)006:1191: rdo rje'i 'khor lo rab tu bskor //
NK005(ca)006:1192: de bzhin du rdo rje'i gnas su /
NK005(ca)006:1197: zhes bsgyur bas rjes su gnang ba sbyin no //
NK005(ca)006:1198: gsum pa lung bstan pa ni /
NK005(ca)006:1199: de bzhin gshegs pa'i spyod lam gyi tshul du chos
NK005(ca)006:1200: gos kyi grwa ri dwags kyi rna ba lta bu
NK005(ca)006:1201: g.yon pa'i khu tshur gyis bzung zhing g.yas pa mi
NK005(ca)006:1202: 'jigs pa'i rgyas / 'di ltar khyod la ngas lung bstan //
NK005(ca)006:1203: rdo rje dpal ldan gsang ba'i bdag /
NK005(ca)006:1204: dngos po mchog tu grub pa'i phyir //
NK005(ca)006:1205: srid pa'i ngan 'gro rnams las grol //
NK005(ca)006:1206: kye che ge mo zhes bya ba'i de bzhin gshegs pa b+hur b+hu wan /
NK005(ca)006:1207: zhes slob dpon gyis lung bstan pa bzhin du dus
NK005(ca)006:1208: gsum gyi rgyal ba rnams kyis phyogs bcu nas gsung
NK005(ca)006:1209: dbyangs mthun pa'i sgra skad kyis lung bstan par mdzad
NK005(ca)006:1210: de / kyee rigs kyi bu khyod kyi srid pa tha ma ni 'di yin te /
NK005(ca)006:1211: gsang ba bla na med pa'i theg pa la zhugs
NK005(ca)006:1212: pas phyag rgya chen po dang gsang sngags kyi mthus
NK005(ca)006:1213: rigs kyi dkyil 'khor du gnas par 'gyur ro //
NK005(ca)006:1214: khyod kyi chags pa gnyis dang bral bar mi bya ste /
NK005(ca)006:1215: de dag gi las la sbyar bar bya'o //
NK005(ca)006:1217: 'dod chags bral ba lta bu'i sdig /
NK005(ca)006:1218: khams gsum na ni gzhan med de //
NK005(ca)006:1219: de bas 'dod la chags bral bar //
NK005(ca)006:1220: khyod kyis nam yang bya ba min //
NK005(ca)006:1221: ma h+aa sa ma ya h+aum phata /
NK005(ca)006:1222: nga ni dkyil 'khor slob dpon te //
NK005(ca)006:1223: sngags dang rgyud rnams 'dzin par gyur //
NK005(ca)006:1224: sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa' dang //
NK005(ca)006:1225: lha rnams kun gyis mthun par gsungs //
NK005(ca)006:1226: sems can rnams la rjes brtse bas //
NK005(ca)006:1227: dkyil 'khor cho ga bzhin du bris //
NK005(ca)006:1228: rtse gcig nan tan bskyed nas ni //
NK005(ca)006:1229: sgrub pa po rnams rgyud la sbyor //
NK005(ca)006:1230: zhes brjod de lung bstan no //
NK005(ca)006:1231: bzhi pa dbugs dbyung ba la bzhi las /
NK005(ca)006:1234: zhugs shing mthong la sogs pa yis //
NK005(ca)006:1235: sdig pa kun las rnam grol zhing //
NK005(ca)006:1236: khyed rnams rab tu bde bar gnas //
NK005(ca)006:1237: zhes dkyil 'khor mthong ba'i phan yon gyis dbugs dbyung ba'o //
NK005(ca)006:1239: bde chen theg pa 'di la ni //
NK005(ca)006:1240: phyin chad 'chi ba yongs med de //
NK005(ca)006:1241: tshugs med thub par mi 'gyur bas //
NK005(ca)006:1242: cis kyang mi 'jigs dga' bar gyis //
NK005(ca)006:1243: srid pa shin tu dag pas na //
NK005(ca)006:1245: zhes don bzhin spyad pa'i phan yon gyis dbugs dbyung ba'o //
NK005(ca)006:1247: rdo rje zhes bya'i phyag rgya ste //
NK005(ca)006:1248: gang zhig bskyed pa tsam gyis ni //
NK005(ca)006:1249: sangs rgyas nyid 'gyur the tshom med //
NK005(ca)006:1250: dam pa'i chos dag mi smad cing //
NK005(ca)006:1251: ma gus spang zhing 'dor mi bya //
NK005(ca)006:1252: mi shes snod min rmongs pa la //
NK005(ca)006:1253: nam yang bstan par mi bya'o //
NK005(ca)006:1254: rdo rje dril bu mi spang ste //
NK005(ca)006:1255: slob dpon dag la gus par gyis //
NK005(ca)006:1256: zhes dam tshig brjod pas dbugs dbyung ba'o //
NK005(ca)006:1258: khams gsum gyi ni rgyal srid che //
NK005(ca)006:1259: bdag por rgyal chen dbang bskur zhing //
NK005(ca)006:1260: bdud rnams kun las rnam rgyal te //
NK005(ca)006:1261: grong khyer mchog tu zhugs pa yin //
NK005(ca)006:1263: sangs rgyas thob par the tshom med //
NK005(ca)006:1264: ces slob dpon gyi dbang thob pa'i phan yon gyis dbugs dbyung ba'o //
NK005(ca)006:1265: lnga pa gdams ngag bstan pa ni /
NK005(ca)006:1266: dkyil 'khor dang lha dang slob dpon gyi de kho na nyid de gsum las /
NK005(ca)006:1268: dkyil 'khor gyi mtshan nyid ni gru bzhi par gnas pas /
NK005(ca)006:1269: che ba'i yon tan thams cad kyis rgyas par byas shing /
NK005(ca)006:1270: sgo rnam pa bzhi yis byams pa dang /
NK005(ca)006:1273: btang snyoms kyi mtshan nyid can no //
NK005(ca)006:1274: rta babs nas chos kyi 'khor lo'i bar du ni
NK005(ca)006:1275: rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba'i tshul du gnas pa
NK005(ca)006:1276: ni byang chub kyi chos sum cu rtsa bdun gyi
NK005(ca)006:1277: bar du bgrod nas rnam par thar pa'i sgo bzhir
NK005(ca)006:1279: rin po che sna lnga'i rtsig pa las 'od kha
NK005(ca)006:1280: dog nyi shu rtsa lnga dang bcas pa 'phro ba
NK005(ca)006:1281: ni / rang bzhin ye shes drug gi byin rlabs
NK005(ca)006:1282: las rigs kyi mtshan ma sna tshogs su snang ba'i
NK005(ca)006:1283: ni / rang bzhin no // rdo rjes mtshan pa'i
NK005(ca)006:1284: ka ba brgyad ni rnam par thar pa brgyad kyi
NK005(ca)006:1285: ni / rang bzhin no // rang bzhin la / rdo rje theg pa'i tshul gyis mtshon pa'o //
NK005(ca)006:1288: me tog gi phreng bas brgyan pa ni mdzad pa
NK005(ca)006:1289: rgya chen po'i phrin las rnams yon tan las byung
NK005(ca)006:1290: ba'i tshul lo // 'dod pa'i yon tan drug gi lha mo ni /
NK005(ca)006:1291: yul drug rnam par dag pa'i snang ba'o //
NK005(ca)006:1292: gdugs snying rje chen po'i char kheb dang /
NK005(ca)006:1293: rgyal mtshan bdud rnam bzhi las rgyal zhing theg pa'i mchog ston pa'i mtshan ma dang /
NK005(ca)006:1294: bla re mnyam pa nyid du tshul gcig par sbyor ba'i tshul /
NK005(ca)006:1295: rnga yab rnam par rtog pa'i sbrang ma sel bar mdzad pa dang /
NK005(ca)006:1296: zla ba phyed pa rdo rjes smon lam rgya chen
NK005(ca)006:1297: po 'gro ba'i don du theg pa chen po'i sngags
NK005(ca)006:1298: kyis sgo nas don mdzad pa dang /
NK005(ca)006:1299: rdo rje rin po che dbyig pa la ba dan
NK005(ca)006:1300: dpyangs pas mtshan dang dpe byad phun sum tshogs pa'i
NK005(ca)006:1302: de nas dril bu sgra snyan pa phyogs bcur sgrogs
NK005(ca)006:1303: pa ni theg pa sna tshogs kyi don ston pa'o
NK005(ca)006:1304: // re'u cha brgyad kyi mtshan ma ni sku'i dbang phyug dang /
NK005(ca)006:1306: thugs kyi dbang phyug la sogs pa'i yon tan brgyad kyis brgyan pa'o //
NK005(ca)006:1307: thig bzhis legs par phye ba ni phrin las bzhi'i snang ba'o //
NK005(ca)006:1308: sna tshogs pad+ma'i mtshan ma dang /
NK005(ca)006:1309: mu khyud rdo rje'i phreng bas bskor ba ni chags
NK005(ca)006:1310: pa med pa'i phrin las kun tu don spyod cing
NK005(ca)006:1311: nyon mongs pa'i mtshan mas ma gos shing bde ba
NK005(ca)006:1312: chen po'i dbyings las sku gsung thugs kyi theg pa
NK005(ca)006:1314: bum pa rgyan gyis mdzes shing bdud rtsi'i bcud dang
NK005(ca)006:1315: ldan pas che ba'i yon tan thams cad kyi 'byung
NK005(ca)006:1316: gnas 'chi ba med pa'i bdud rtsi ye shes rnam
NK005(ca)006:1317: pa lnga'i don las yon tan gyi snang ba ma
NK005(ca)006:1318: 'gags shing 'dod pa'i longs spyod sna tshogs su 'phro
NK005(ca)006:1319: ba'o // bar du re'u mig 'khor lo'i tshul du
NK005(ca)006:1320: gnas pa ni phrin las dang mchod pa'i gnas su
NK005(ca)006:1321: gyur cing rang gi phyag rgya mdzes par gyur pa'o
NK005(ca)006:1322: ba'o // // phyi rol pad+ma la sogs pa'i phreng
NK005(ca)006:1323: ba dag ni chos thams cad rnam par dag pa'i
NK005(ca)006:1324: yon tan gyi snang ba ston pa dang /
NK005(ca)006:1325: sku gsung thugs kyi phrin las dang bcas pa'i rnam pa dang /
NK005(ca)006:1326: ye shes kyi byin rlabs kyis mi mthun pa'i rnam par rtog pa thams cad sel bar mdzad pa'o //
NK005(ca)006:1327: phyi rol gyi dur khrod chen po dag gis ni
NK005(ca)006:1328: thams cad gsang sngags ni theg par 'du zhing theg
NK005(ca)006:1329: pa gzhan las khyad par du 'phags pa'i tshul khams
NK005(ca)006:1330: gsum gyi zhen rtog sbyang ba dang /
NK005(ca)006:1331: phung po lnga dang 'byung ba lnga rnam par dag pa'i ngo bor bstan pa'o //
NK005(ca)006:1332: zhing dang zhing skyong dag gis yon tan ma 'gags
NK005(ca)006:1333: pa'i rten la sangs rgyas brgyad kyi snang ba ston
NK005(ca)006:1334: pa'o // mtsho dang klu brgyad ni srid pa'i gnas
NK005(ca)006:1335: kyi rtog pa'i tshogs dag gnyis su med pa'i byang
NK005(ca)006:1336: chub kyi sems kyi don ston pa'o //
NK005(ca)006:1337: rnal 'byor pho mo dag gis ni dbyings dang ye
NK005(ca)006:1338: shes zung du 'brel ba'i don gyis chos thams cad
NK005(ca)006:1340: sprin dang mchod rten la sogs pa'i rnam pa dag
NK005(ca)006:1341: gis ni thugs rje chen po'i sprul pa'i 'phro 'du
NK005(ca)006:1342: dang ye shes kyi snang ba brgyad bstan pa'o //
NK005(ca)006:1343: bya khyi dang mkha' 'gro la sogs pa sna tshogs pas ni thugs rje chen po'i sprul pa dang /
NK005(ca)006:1344: yon tan gyi rtsal ma 'gags pa'i phrin las kyi tshogs rnam par 'phro ba bstan pa yin no //
NK005(ca)006:1345: de ltar rten gyi mtshan nyid rnams shes par byas nas /
NK005(ca)006:1346: gnyis pa brten pa'i rang bzhin ni /
NK005(ca)006:1347: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' dkar dmar gyi mdangs dang
NK005(ca)006:1348: ldan pas byang chub kyi sems kyi rang bzhin la
NK005(ca)006:1349: rtog pa'i mtshan mas ma gos shing thugs rje chen
NK005(ca)006:1350: pos chags pa'i las mdzad pa'o //
NK005(ca)006:1351: rin po che'i kha dog sna lnga'i 'od zer mdzes
NK005(ca)006:1352: pas brgyan pa ni ye shes rnam pa lnga'i snang
NK005(ca)006:1353: ba las rigs kyi mtshan ma sna tshogs ston pa'o
NK005(ca)006:1355: phyag bzhi'i rnam pa can du byung bas phrin las rnam pa bzhi dang /
NK005(ca)006:1356: tshad med pa dag gi sgo nas 'gro ba dbugs 'byin pa'o //
NK005(ca)006:1357: sgeg pa la sogs pa'i tshul gyis khams gsum las rgyal zhing /
NK005(ca)006:1358: rang gi cha lugs bcom par mdzad pa'o //
NK005(ca)006:1359: phyag bzhi'i mtshon cha dag gis ye shes rnam pa
NK005(ca)006:1360: lnga'i che ba las rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor snang bar
NK005(ca)006:1361: mdzad pa dang / thugs rje chen pos rtse gcig tu sems kyi las la dgongs pa dang /
NK005(ca)006:1362: sku gsung thugs sna tshogs kyi sgo nas khams gsum las rgyal te /
NK005(ca)006:1363: gsang ba bla na med pa'i tshul ston pa dang /
NK005(ca)006:1364: zhi gnas dang lhag mthong zung du 'brel ba'i las kyis bskul ba dang /
NK005(ca)006:1365: de'i mtshan nyid gzhan la ston par mdzad pa'o //
NK005(ca)006:1366: mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis dang dpe byad
NK005(ca)006:1367: bzang po brgyad cu dag gzhan las khyad par du
NK005(ca)006:1368: 'phags pa'i tshul gyis mdzes shing byang chub sems kyi
NK005(ca)006:1369: mchog tu gyur pa'i thugs rje chen po'i rnam pa
NK005(ca)006:1370: dang ma bral ba'i sgo nas stod g.yogs dang /
NK005(ca)006:1371: mdzad pa sna tshogs kyi las mnga' bas smad g.yogs kyi brgyan pa'o //
NK005(ca)006:1372: bsdu ba'i dngos po bzhi dang /
NK005(ca)006:1373: tshad med pa bzhi'i phrin las dag la spyod pas dpung pa rin po ches mdzes pa'o //
NK005(ca)006:1374: gzhan yang rin po che'i ske rags dang /
NK005(ca)006:1376: do shal gyis dge ba bcu dang /
NK005(ca)006:1377: pha rol tu phyin pa bcu dang /
NK005(ca)006:1378: sangs rgyas kyi chos ma 'dres pa bco brgyad dang /
NK005(ca)006:1379: byang chub kyi phyogs kyi chos sum cu rtsa bdun gyi don ston par byed pa'o //
NK005(ca)006:1380: phyag dang zhabs la gdu bus mdzes shing se mo do bcus mtshan pa ni bden pa bzhi dang /
NK005(ca)006:1381: rnam par thar pa brgyad dang /
NK005(ca)006:1382: dge ba bcu yongs su rdzogs pa'i rtags so //
NK005(ca)006:1383: dbu la rin po che'i rgyan dang /
NK005(ca)006:1386: rigs kyi bdag po dag gis brgyan pa ni pha rol tu phyin pa drug dang /
NK005(ca)006:1387: rigs rnam pa lnga dang rigs kyi mtshan mas lhag par gyur pa'o //
NK005(ca)006:1388: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje dang /
NK005(ca)006:1390: sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor gyis brgyan pa ni phyag
NK005(ca)006:1391: rgya bzhi'i sgo nas de nyid kyi don bstan par
NK005(ca)006:1392: mdzad pa dang / phung po lnga rnam par dag pa'i rang bzhin du bzhags pa'o //
NK005(ca)006:1393: gzhan yang 'byung ba rnam pa bzhi rnam par dag
NK005(ca)006:1394: pa'i sgo nas khyad par gyi phrin las bzhis 'gro
NK005(ca)006:1395: ba'i don bya ba'i phyir rigs kyi lha mo bzhi
NK005(ca)006:1396: dang / skye mched la sogs pa zag pa dang
NK005(ca)006:1397: bcas pa rnam par dag par mdzad cing rigs dang
NK005(ca)006:1398: ye shes kyi snang ba yon tan gyi tshogs rnam
NK005(ca)006:1399: par 'phrul pa las byung ba'i phrin las kyis gzhan
NK005(ca)006:1400: gyi don mdzad pa'i phyir phrin las sna tshogs dang
NK005(ca)006:1401: bcas par bstan pa yin no //
NK005(ca)006:1404: dgug mchod las sbyor bsrung ba che //
NK005(ca)006:1405: nyer bsdu gshegs su gsol ba yi //
NK005(ca)006:1406: de nyid bcu la sogs la mkhas //
NK005(ca)006:1407: khyad par las kyi rim pa yis //
NK005(ca)006:1408: gsal mdzad rgya chen 'gro ba dmigs //
NK005(ca)006:1409: zhes slob dpon gyi de kho na nyid de /
NK005(ca)006:1410: de ltar bcu ni slob dpon gyi bya ba'o //
NK005(ca)006:1411: de ltar phyi gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor du bum pa'i dbang bskur ba tho ba pas /
NK005(ca)006:1412: ji ltar snang ba thams cad lha'i 'khor lor rtogs
NK005(ca)006:1413: pa'i bde ba chen po'i ye shes mngon du bya
NK005(ca)006:1414: ba'o // gnyis pa nang gi dbang ni /
NK005(ca)006:1415: dris byugs shing me tog bkram pa'i gnas dben par bde ba'i stan la slob dpon 'khod pa la /
NK005(ca)006:1416: shes rab mtshan ldan yon dang bcas pa phul /
NK005(ca)006:1417: tshogs kyi 'khor lo'i mchod pas mnyes par byas nas man+dala phul te /
NK005(ca)006:1418: dpal ldan mgon po bde ba che //
NK005(ca)006:1419: bde chen bde ba'i gnas la bzhugs //
NK005(ca)006:1420: sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK005(ca)006:1421: mkha' 'gro sgyu ma'i bde stsol mdzad //
NK005(ca)006:1422: byang chub sems dpa' che rnams kyi //
NK005(ca)006:1423: yang dag don mchog rnam dag pa //
NK005(ca)006:1424: ji ltar de nyid bdud rtsi yis //
NK005(ca)006:1425: mchog gi dbang ni bskur ba bzhin //
NK005(ca)006:1426: de bzhin bdag sogs 'gro kun gyi //
NK005(ca)006:1427: sdug bsngal thams cad sel bar mdzod //
NK005(ca)006:1428: rnal 'byor bdud rtsi dri med mchog /
NK005(ca)006:1429: ma rig rtog pa'i rab rib bsal //
NK005(ca)006:1430: gang gi byang chub bla med pa //
NK005(ca)006:1431: de ring bdag gis thob par mdzod //
NK005(ca)006:1432: ces lan gsum gyis gsol ba btab /
NK005(ca)006:1434: bu khyod ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin //
NK005(ca)006:1435: rgyal ba kun gyi bde chen sbyin //
NK005(ca)006:1437: de nas phyi nang gi khrus sogs kyis dam tshig gi lha mo sbyangs /
NK005(ca)006:1438: sngags dang bcas pa'i yungs kar gyis bgegs bskrad /
NK005(ca)006:1439: rang nyid bcom ldan 'das rdo rje sems dpa' dang
NK005(ca)006:1440: phyag rgya mtshan nyid thams cad rdzogs pa shes rab
NK005(ca)006:1441: kyi pha rol tu phyin par gyur /
NK005(ca)006:1442: rjes su chags pa'i rnam mang bde ba'i pad+mo rnams //
NK005(ca)006:1443: dga' ba'i mchod pas gsal bar rjes su mchod byas pas //
NK005(ca)006:1444: mchog tu rtag pa'i rnal 'byor bde bas bde grub mdzod //
NK005(ca)006:1445: e ma ho mchog tu bde ba'i dam tshig ngo bo nyid //
NK005(ca)006:1446: mchog tu bde ba'i rnal 'byor skal bzang mchog dgyes pa //
NK005(ca)006:1447: rang gi dam tshig rtag par rol cig rol cig pa'o //
NK005(ca)006:1448: zhes pa'i glu len sngon du 'gro bas /
NK005(ca)006:1449: yab kyi gsang gnas h+aum las rdo rje 'bar ba nor bu'i rtse mor can phata kyis mtshan pa /
NK005(ca)006:1450: yum gyi gsang gnas +aahls pad+ma ser po 'dab ma
NK005(ca)006:1451: brgyad pa phyi rol chos 'byung gi dbyibs can +aahs
NK005(ca)006:1452: mtshan pa'o // stong pa shin tu yod med rnal 'byor mthus //
NK005(ca)006:1453: nam mkha' bzhin las dam tshig nye bar gnas //
NK005(ca)006:1454: ye shes rgya mtsho rnam par grol ba'i klong //
NK005(ca)006:1455: mi gnas mi dmigs chos kyi dbyings nas bzhengs //
NK005(ca)006:1458: sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK005(ca)006:1459: dzahh+aum bam hoh pra be sha ya phata /
NK005(ca)006:1460: a la la hoh zhes snyoms par zhugs pas bde
NK005(ca)006:1461: ba chen po'i 'od zer gyis sangs rgyas thams cad
NK005(ca)006:1462: mnyes shing bskul / sems can thams cad kyi dri ma sbyangs nas /
NK005(ca)006:1463: lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes kyi rten du gyur
NK005(ca)006:1464: pa kun+da byang chub kyi sems mtheb srin gyis blangs
NK005(ca)006:1465: nas slob bu'i lce thog tu bzhag ste /
NK005(ca)006:1466: ji ltar rgyal ba bde gshegs kyis //
NK005(ca)006:1467: rang gi sras mchog dbang bskur bzhin //
NK005(ca)006:1468: byang chub sems de dag pa'i chus //
NK005(ca)006:1469: rtog pa'i dri ma dag par bya //
NK005(ca)006:1470: ma h+aa bo d+hi tsit+ta sa ma ya a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK005(ca)006:1471: zhes brjod pa dang slob mas /
NK005(ca)006:1473: zhes mid de longs spyod kyi gnas su zhugs pas dus gsum gyi rnam rtog dag /
NK005(ca)006:1474: rigs kyi cha lugs gsal ba chu'i zla ba'am /
NK005(ca)006:1475: sgyu ma'i rnam pa bzhin du gnas pa'i gsal stong
NK005(ca)006:1476: nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i ting nge 'dzin rgyud la
NK005(ca)006:1478: de ltar bla ma'i lus kyi dkyil 'khor du gsang ba'i dbang bskur ba thob /
NK005(ca)006:1479: sgyu ma chu zla lta bur bdag byin gyis brlab
NK005(ca)006:1480: pa'i bde mchog gi ye shes mngon du byas pa'o
NK005(ca)006:1482: gsum pa gsang ba'i dbang ni /
NK005(ca)006:1483: rdzogs pa'i rim pa 'dod pas man+dala dang mchod pa'i tshogs kyis bla ma mnyes par byas nas /
NK005(ca)006:1484: kye kye mgon po bde ba che //
NK005(ca)006:1485: rdo rje sbyor las yang dag byung //
NK005(ca)006:1486: mi phyed phyag rgya rab bsgrub pa //
NK005(ca)006:1487: mngon sum nyams myong bskyed pa'i phyir //
NK005(ca)006:1488: bdag nyid che khyod ci lta bar //
NK005(ca)006:1489: gtso bos bdag la bka' drin mdzod //
NK005(ca)006:1490: rtog pa'i dri mas bsgrib pa rnams //
NK005(ca)006:1491: byang chub chu yis dag par mdzod //
NK005(ca)006:1492: ces lan gsum gyis gsol ba gdab /
NK005(ca)006:1493: des kyang rigs dang mthun pa'i phyag rgya gzugs dang
NK005(ca)006:1494: lang tsho phun sum tshogs pa slob ma'i lag pa
NK005(ca)006:1495: g.yon par phyag rgya'i lag g.yas gtad de /
NK005(ca)006:1496: de ltar bla ma'i lag g.yon pas bzung nas /
NK005(ca)006:1497: dga' ba'i gnas chen lha mo 'di //
NK005(ca)006:1498: sna tshogs sgyu rtsal yid du 'ong //
NK005(ca)006:1499: legs par zungs shig blo gros can //
NK005(ca)006:1500: dga' bde'i mchod pa rab tu gyis //
NK005(ca)006:1501: thabs gzhan gyis ni 'tshang mi rgya //
NK005(ca)006:1503: de bas khyod kyis 'di nyid dang //
NK005(ca)006:1504: nam yang 'bral bar mi bya ste //
NK005(ca)006:1505: 'di ni sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK005(ca)006:1506: rig pa'i brtul zhugs bla na med //
NK005(ca)006:1507: blun po gang zhig 'di spong ba //
NK005(ca)006:1508: de la mchog gi dngos grub med //
NK005(ca)006:1509: ces brjod de byin pa dang /
NK005(ca)006:1510: lha mos de la dga' ba'i bzhin gyis bltas te
NK005(ca)006:1511: 'dzum pa dang bcas pas b+ha ga phye ba bstan
NK005(ca)006:1512: nas / khyod kyis nus sam rdo rje can //
NK005(ca)006:1513: dri chen dri chu'i bza' btung dang //
NK005(ca)006:1514: rak+ta ga bur m+aam sa dang //
NK005(ca)006:1515: bud med rnams la rtag gus dang //
NK005(ca)006:1516: b+ha gar 'o byed mi rtog gam //
NK005(ca)006:1517: smos shig grogs po dge ba can //
NK005(ca)006:1520: lha mo ci phyir bdag mi spro //
NK005(ca)006:1521: khu khrag la sogs za ba dang //
NK005(ca)006:1522: bud med rnams la rtag gus shing //
NK005(ca)006:1525: de nas lha mo'i gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor gsal bar bstan nas /
NK005(ca)006:1527: thams cad bde bar yang dag ldan //
NK005(ca)006:1528: rtag tu rim bzhin 'di spyod na //
NK005(ca)006:1529: de nyid bde chen bral mi 'gyur //
NK005(ca)006:1530: chos dbyings 'di ni rnam par dag /
NK005(ca)006:1531: sems can thams cad rab grol byed //
NK005(ca)006:1532: bde chen rgyal po 'di nyid ni //
NK005(ca)006:1533: dngos po kun gyi rang bzhin gnas //
NK005(ca)006:1534: nang gi rtsa yi 'khor lo'i tshogs //
NK005(ca)006:1535: pad+ma la zhugs rab tu rgyas //
NK005(ca)006:1536: b+ha ga'i mkha' dbyings nam mkha' bzhin //
NK005(ca)006:1537: 'byung ba bzhi po rgyan bzhin bkod //
NK005(ca)006:1538: lte ba'i ze'u 'bru ge sar zlum //
NK005(ca)006:1539: 'dab ma brgyad sogs rnam par mdzes //
NK005(ca)006:1540: de yi dbus na gnas pa ni //
NK005(ca)006:1541: de nyid bdud rtsi bde chen bzung //
